{"type":"message","id":"a71bf317","parentId":"00248593","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:09:57.475Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The connection to composio timed out. This might be a network issue. Let me explain the usage to the user anyway, and mention the connection issue.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n连接超时了 😅（Composio 服务器暂时连不上，可能是网络问题）\n\n不过用法是这样的：\n\n### 调用工具\n\n```bash\n# 列出所有可用工具\nmcporter list composio\n\n# 查看具体工具的参数\nmcporter list composio --schema\n\n# 调用工具\nmcporter call composio.<工具名> 参数\n```\n\n### 示例\n\n```bash\n# 假设有个 create_task 工具\nmcporter call composio.create_task title=\"My Task\" priority=high\n\n# 或用 JSON 参数\nmcporter call composio.list_items --args '{\"limit\": 10}'\n```\n\nComposio 是一个 **AI 集成平台**，连接了 250+ 第三方服务（GitHub、Linear、Slack、Notion 等）。你可以让它帮你操作这些第三方工具。\n\n等网络恢复后可以再试试 `mcporter list composio` 看具体有哪些工具。需要我重试一下吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":17282,"output":218,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17500,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775646594244,"responseId":"chatcmpl-db9f7ce3-2626-4b30-aefc-2c07928602fb"}}
