{"type":"message","id":"df1c7a18","parentId":"1358853c","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:12:23.189Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在有不同了！返回了 405 错误，说明服务器是可达的，但是需要认证。错误说 \"run 'mcporter auth composio' to finish authentication.\"\n\n需要让用户进行认证。让我看看 auth 命令怎么用。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这次不同了！服务器可达，但返回 **405 错误**——需要认证。\n\n试试运行：\n\n```bash\nmcporter auth composio\n```\n\n如果需要 API Key，你可能要用：\n\n```bash\nmcporter auth composio --reset\n# 然后按提示输入 API Key\n```\n\n或者如果你的 Composio 账户只需要那个 header 里的 key，可能需要用另一种方式配置。要我帮你查一下正确的认证方式吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":16569,"output":137,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17858,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775646735100,"responseId":"019d6cca669aa533a23eeb67b506e27a"}}
