{"type":"message","id":"0e146fa8","parentId":"6abfadd5","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:16:43.894Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"有趣！curl 成功返回了，但返回了 401 错误。\n\n关键信息在 `www-authenticate` header 里：\n```\nwww-authenticate: Bearer error=\"unauthorized\", error_description=\"Missing authentication: provide Authorization: Bearer or x-consumer-api-key header\"\n```\n\n所以实际上，Composio 的这个端点**确实需要 `x-consumer-api-key` header**！\n\n我之前改成了 `x-api-key` 是错的。让我改回去，但这次试试用 Authorization: Bearer 的方式，或者继续用 x-consumer-api-key。\n\n让我试试：\n1. 用 x-consumer-api-key\n2. 看看是否需要 Bearer token 格式\n\n实际上 curl 返回 401 说明服务器可达了！问题是认证。让我看看错误信息 - 它说需要 \"Authorization: Bearer\" 或 \"x-consumer-api-key\" header。\n\n让我改回去用 x-consumer-api-key 试试，但可能还需要其他认证方式...\n\n用户一开始给的就是 x-consumer-api-key，可能需要 Bearer token。让我查看一下。\n\n先改回 x-consumer-api-key 试试：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n有意思！curl 返回了 **401**，但说明：\n\n> 需要 `Authorization: Bearer` 或 `x-consumer-api-key` header\n\n说明你的 key 格式可能需要 Bearer token。让我试试：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6ccf01509911963f6df367ea899e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter config remove composio && mcporter config add composio --url https://connect.composio.dev/mcp --header \"Authorization=Bearer ck_8edc9fR2KGT5BrcHiA1Y\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3882,"output":320,"cacheRead":17536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21738,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775646987419,"responseId":"019d6ccecdec59698e46499e044af4b3"}}
