{"type":"message","id":"97582965","parentId":"d5a49fd3","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:26:14.465Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"mcporter 仍然报 405 错误。这是因为 mcporter 默认使用 SSE（Server-Send Events）方式连接，但 Composio 需要 POST 方式请求。\n\n不过直接用 curl 调用是可以的，所以问题出在 mcporter 的连接方式上。让我看看能否强制使用不同的 transport。\n\n根据之前查的帮助信息，可以指定 `--transport` 参数来强制特定的传输方式。但问题是 Composio 需要 POST 请求，而 SSE 方式可能不工作...\n\n让我先检查一下当前的配置，然后尝试使用 mcporter 的 call 命令直接调用工具（跳过 list）。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8e70d81eb2bd493e97a06f5f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mcporter config get composio"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":50245,"output":140,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50385,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775647569497,"responseId":"chatcmpl-3d5d4f26-9114-4f2a-aa22-bd1ddd641217"}}
