{"type":"message","id":"95505192","parentId":"0d99590e","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:29:01.598Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，共有42个GitHub工具。让我给用户一个清晰的列表。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nComposio MCP 当前配置有 **42 个 GitHub 工具**：\n\n### 📋 工具列表\n\n| 类别 | 工具 |\n|------|------|\n| **仓库** | `GITHUB_CREATE_AN_ORGANIZATION_REPOSITORY`, `GITHUB_DELETE_A_REPOSITORY`, `GITHUB_GET_REPOSITORY_CONTENT`, `GITHUB_LIST_BRANCHES`, `GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORY_WORKFLOWS` |\n| **文件** | `GITHUB_CREATE_OR_UPDATE_FILE_CONTENTS`, `GITHUB_CREATE_A_BLOB`, `GITHUB_COMMIT_MULTIPLE_FILES`, `GITHUB_GET_A_TREE`, `GITHUB_CREATE_A_TREE` |\n| **分支/标签** | `GITHUB_CREATE_A_REFERENCE`, `GITHUB_UPDATE_A_REFERENCE`, `GITHUB_GET_A_REFERENCE` |\n| **Issue** | `GITHUB_CREATE_AN_ISSUE`, `GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORY_ISSUES`, `GITHUB_ADD_ASSIGNEES_TO_AN_ISSUE`, `GITHUB_ADD_LABELS_TO_AN_ISSUE`, `GITHUB_CREATE_AN_ISSUE_COMMENT` |\n| **PR** | `GITHUB_CREATE_A_PULL_REQUEST`, `GITHUB_LIST_PULL_REQUESTS`, `GITHUB_FIND_PULL_REQUESTS`, `GITHUB_GET_A_PULL_REQUEST`, `GITHUB_LIST_PULL_REQUESTS_FILES`, `GITHUB_APPROVE_WORKFLOW_RUN_FOR_FORK_PULL_REQUEST` |\n| **搜索** | `GITHUB_FIND_REPOSITORIES`, `GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORIES_FOR_THE_AUTHENTICATED_USER`, `GITHUB_LIST_STARGAZERS`, `GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORY_CONTRIBUTORS` |\n| **用户/组织** | `GITHUB_LIST_ORGANIZATIONS_FOR_THE_AUTHENTICATED_USER`, `GITHUB_LIST_ORGANIZATIONS_FOR_A_USER`, `GITHUB_ADD_A_REPOSITORY_COLLABORATOR` |\n| **Release** | `GITHUB_CREATE_A_RELEASE` |\n| **其他** | `GITHUB_LIST_NOTIFICATIONS`, `GITHUB_STAR_A_REPOSITORY_FOR_THE_AUTHENTICATED_USER`, `GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORIES_STARRED_BY_THE_AUTHENTICATED_USER`, `GITHUB_LIST_CHECK_RUNS_FOR_A_REF`, `GITHUB_LIST_DEPLOYMENTS`, `GITHUB_LIST_SECRET_SCANNING_ALERTS_FOR_A_REPOSITORY`, `GITHUB_CREATE_DRAFT_ITEM_FOR_USER_PROJECT`, `GITHUB_COMPARE_TWO_COMMITS`, `GITHUB_CREATE_A_COMMIT`, `GITHUB_ADD_EMAIL_ADDRESS_FOR_AUTHENTICATED_USER` |\n\n### 调用示例\n\n```bash\nmcporter call \"composio.GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORIES_FOR_THE_AUTHENTICATED_USER\" per_page=10\nmcporter call \"composio.GITHUB_CREATE_AN_ISSUE\" owner=my-org repo=my-repo title=\"New bug\"\n```\n\n需要我帮你测试哪个操作吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":61241,"output":688,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61929,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775647732749,"responseId":"chatcmpl-c48ed94b-47db-4ed7-b1a6-1be6bceb394b"}}
