{"type":"message","id":"9dd8b8b9","parentId":"2386a467","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:34:20.983Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking how to use the Composio MCP server. Let me explain in a clear way.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 使用方式\n\n#### 1. 命令行直接调用\n\n```bash\n# 列出你的仓库\nmcporter call \"composio.GITHUB_LIST_REPOSITORIES_FOR_THE_AUTHENTICATED_USER\" per_page=10\n\n# 创建 Issue\nmcporter call \"composio.GITHUB_CREATE_AN_ISSUE\" owner=你的org repo=你的仓库 title=\"Bug: XXX\"\n\n# 创建 PR\nmcporter call \"composio.GITHUB_CREATE_A_PULL_REQUEST\" owner=xxx repo=xxx base=main head=feature-branch title=\"Feature: XXX\"\n\n# 上传文件\nmcporter call \"composio.GITHUB_CREATE_OR_UPDATE_FILE_CONTENTS\" owner=xxx repo=xxx path=\"README.md\" content=\"# Hello\" branch=main\n```\n\n#### 2. 在 OpenClaw 里让我帮你操作\n\n直接告诉我你想做什么，例如：\n- \"帮我创建一个 GitHub issue\"\n- \"列出我的仓库\"\n- \"创建一个 PR\"\n\n我来帮你调用。\n\n---\n\n⚠️ 注意：当前环境网络连不上 Composio，但**在你的环境里**应该能正常使用。你是在哪个环境运行？是本地还是 VPS？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":48853,"output":264,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49117,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775648055005,"responseId":"chatcmpl-89a6f060-1152-480b-bcd7-26e3d5a63c64"}}
