{"type":"message","id":"33e7a7af","parentId":"94c2b54a","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:42:26.232Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！memU 是 NevaMind-AI 的一个项目，是为 OpenClaw (原 ClawDBot) 设计的长期记忆引擎。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！**memU** 是 NevaMind-AI 开发的 **AI 主动记忆引擎**：\n\n### 主要项目\n\n| 仓库 | 描述 | ⭐ | 语言 |\n|------|------|---:|------|\n| **[NevaMind-AI/memU](https://github.com/NevaMind-AI/memU)** | 24/7 主动 AI 记忆系统，为 OpenClaw/ClawDBot 设计 | 13.3k | Python |\n| **[NevaMind-AI/memUBot](https://github.com/NevaMind-AI/memUBot)** | Enterprise Ready OpenClaw 版本 | 365 | TypeScript |\n| **[NevaMind-AI/memU-server](http://memu.bot)** | memU 后端 | 46 | Python |\n| **[NevaMind-AI/memU-ui](https://github.com/NevaMind-AI/memU-ui)** | memU Web UI | 55 | TypeScript |\n| **[duxiaoxiong/memu-engine-for-OpenClaw](https://github.com/duxiaoxiong/memu-engine-for-OpenClaw)** | OpenClaw 的社区 memory 插件 | 58 | Python |\n\n---\n\n**一句话**：memU 是给 OpenClaw/Claude Code 这些 24/7 运行的 AI 助手用的**长期记忆系统**，让 AI 能主动记住会话历史、偏好、知识，网址是 https://memu.pro\n\n想安装使用吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5005,"output":343,"cacheRead":51200,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56548,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775648529688,"responseId":"019d6ce5943fe87c32c7c0851889320a"}}
