{"type":"message","id":"1be16d6b","parentId":"9da03c98","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:43:58.817Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我看看这两个技能的描述，看看是否与 memU 冲突。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1605211d8ab3477a86f9ab1a","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -30 ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/SKILL.md ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":56950,"output":71,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57021,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775648636591,"responseId":"chatcmpl-7e41083b-892b-45f7-8329-5040acf750aa"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e5fecbad","parentId":"1be16d6b","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:43:58.893Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1605211d8ab3477a86f9ab1a","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"==> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/SKILL.md <==\n---\nname: elite-longterm-memory\nversion: 1.2.3\ndescription: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\nauthor: NextFrontierBuilds\nkeywords: [memory, ai-agent, ai-coding, long-term-memory, vector-search, lancedb, git-notes, wal, persistent-context, claude, claude-code, gpt, chatgpt, cursor, copilot, github-copilot, openclaw, moltbot, vibe-coding, agentic, ai-tools, developer-tools, devtools, typescript, llm, automation]\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: \"🧠\"\n    requires:\n      env:\n        - OPENAI_API_KEY\n      plugins:\n        - memory-lancedb\n---\n\n# Elite Longterm Memory 🧠\n\n**The ultimate memory system for AI agents.** Combines 6 proven approaches into one bulletproof architecture.\n\nNever lose context. Never forget decisions. Never repeat mistakes.\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    ELITE LONGTERM MEMORY                        │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐             │\n\n==> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/SKILL.md <==\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n\n定期整理和优化长期记忆系统。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n1. **扫描** - 读取 `memory/` 下所有文件\n2. **去重** - 合并重复信息\n3. **清理** - 删除过期条目（根据 `[expires: YYYY-MM-DD]` 标记）\n4. **提取** - 将 `ephemeral/` 中有价值的信息迁移到主记忆\n5. **更新** - 刷新 `MEMORY.md` 的 `last_updated` 时间戳\n\n## 触发方式\n\n```bash\n# 手动运行\n~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh\n\n# 或通过 cron 每日运行\n# 建议时间: 每天 04:00 (维护脚本之后)\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n每日日志 (memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":44,"aggregated":"==> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/elite-longterm-memory/SKILL.md <==\n---\nname: elite-longterm-memory\nversion: 1.2.3\ndescription: \"Ultimate AI agent memory system for Cursor, Claude, ChatGPT & Copilot. WAL protocol + vector search + git-notes + cloud backup. Never lose context again. Vibe-coding ready.\"\nauthor: NextFrontierBuilds\nkeywords: [memory, ai-agent, ai-coding, long-term-memory, vector-search, lancedb, git-notes, wal, persistent-context, claude, claude-code, gpt, chatgpt, cursor, copilot, github-copilot, openclaw, moltbot, vibe-coding, agentic, ai-tools, developer-tools, devtools, typescript, llm, automation]\nmetadata:\n  openclaw:\n    emoji: \"🧠\"\n    requires:\n      env:\n        - OPENAI_API_KEY\n      plugins:\n        - memory-lancedb\n---\n\n# Elite Longterm Memory 🧠\n\n**The ultimate memory system for AI agents.** Combines 6 proven approaches into one bulletproof architecture.\n\nNever lose context. Never forget decisions. Never repeat mistakes.\n\n## Architecture Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                    ELITE LONGTERM MEMORY                        │\n├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤\n│                                                                 │\n│  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐  ┌─────────────┐             │\n\n==> /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/memory-keeper/SKILL.md <==\n# Memory Keeper Agent\n\n> 自动化记忆维护 Agent\n\n## 用途\n\n定期整理和优化长期记忆系统。\n\n## 核心职责\n\n1. **扫描** - 读取 `memory/` 下所有文件\n2. **去重** - 合并重复信息\n3. **清理** - 删除过期条目（根据 `[expires: YYYY-MM-DD]` 标记）\n4. **提取** - 将 `ephemeral/` 中有价值的信息迁移到主记忆\n5. **更新** - 刷新 `MEMORY.md` 的 `last_updated` 时间戳\n\n## 触发方式\n\n```bash\n# 手动运行\n~/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/memory_keeper.sh\n\n# 或通过 cron 每日运行\n# 建议时间: 每天 04:00 (维护脚本之后)\n```\n\n## 工作流程\n\n```\n每日日志 (memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md)","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775648638883}}
{"type":"message","id":"ca9ac18b","parentId":"e5fecbad","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:44:18.314Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我看到现有的 memory 相关技能：\n\n1. **elite-longterm-memory** - 一个综合的长期记忆系统，结合了 WAL 协议 + 向量搜索 + git-notes + 云备份等多种方法\n2. **memory-keeper** - 自动化记忆维护 Agent，定期整理和优化长期记忆\n\nmemU 是 NevaMind-AI 开发的另一个 AI 记忆系统。理论上它们可能功能重叠，但：\n\n1. elite-longterm-memory 是第三方 skill (NextFrontierBuilds 开发)\n2. memU 是 NevaMind-AI 开发的，看起来是独立的系统\n\n不一定会冲突，因为：\n- 它们可以用不同的存储后端\n- 可以共存\n- 但可能会重复存储记忆\n\n让我给用户一个清晰的分析。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n让我对比一下：\n\n### 现有 Memory 技能\n\n| 技能 | 功能 | 后端 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **elite-longterm-memory** | 综合记忆系统 (WAL + 向量搜索 + git-notes + 云备份) | LanceDB + Git |\n| **memory-keeper** | 自动化记忆维护 (去重/清理/迁移) | 文件系统 |\n\n### memU\n\n- **定位**: 24/7 主动 AI 记忆引擎 (OpenClaw/ClawDBot 专用)\n- **特点**: 主动记忆 + MCP 协议\n- **官网**: https://memu.pro\n\n---\n\n### 结论：可能会重复\n\n它们都在做「长期记忆」，但实现不同：\n\n- **现有技能**: 基于本地文件/LanceDB\n- **memU**: 自己的服务端 + MCP\n\n**潜在冲突**：\n- 可能导致记忆存储两份（本地 + memU 服务）\n- 记忆重复/不一致\n\n**建议**：\n1. 如果想用 memU，先停用或移除 `elite-longterm-memory`\n2. 或者只用现有技能，暂不接入 memU\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1139,"output":389,"cacheRead":56448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775648638894,"responseId":"019d6ce75abe3ff5ea1c5cbc5147f8bf"}}
