nt-fun/browser-pilot\\\",\\\"has_discussions\\\":false,\\\"has_downloads\\\":true,\\\"has_issues\\\":true,\\\"has_pages\\\":false,\\\"has_projects\\\":true,\\\"has_wiki\\\":true,\\\"homepage\\\":null,\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/agent-fun/browser-pilot\\\",\\\"id\\\":1137500553,\\\"is_template\\\":false,\\\"language\\\":\\\"Fluent\\\",\\\"license\\\":null,\\\"mirror_url\\\":null,\\\"name\\\":\\\"browser-pilot\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"R_kgDOQ8zhiQ\\\",\\\"open_issues\\\":0,\\\"open_issues_count\\\":0,\\\"owner\\\":{\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/255880907?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/agent-fun\\\",\\\"id\\\":255880907,\\\"login\\\":\\\"agent-fun\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"O_kgDOD0Buyw\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\"},\\\"permissions\\\":{\\\"admin\\\":false,\\\"maintain\\\":false,\\\"pull\\\":true,\\\"push\\\":false,\\\"triage\\\":false},\\\"private\\\":false,\\\"pushed_at\\\":\\\"2026-02-03T08:32:38Z\\\",\\\"score\\\":1,\\\"size\\\":10590,\\\"stargazers_count\\\":193,\\\"topics\\\":[],\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-04-01T13:24:03Z\\\",\\\"visibility\\\":\\\"public\\\",\\\"watchers\\\":193,\\\"watchers_count\\\":193,\\\"web_commit_signoff_required\\\":false},{\\\"allow_forking\\\":true,\\\"archived\\\":false,\\\"created_at\\\":\\\"2025-02-25T19:06:23Z\\\",\\\"default_branch\\\":\\\"main\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"AI-driven web automation agent that uses Playwright for browser interactions and LLM integration for intelligent decision-making. It's designed for reliable, adaptable web automation with robust element detection and contextual understanding. It's single agent by design, and it is built with getting solid benefit out of smaller models in mind.\\\",\\\"disabled\\\":false,\\\"fork\\\":false,\\\"forks\\\":28,\\\"forks_count\\\":28,\\\"full_name\\\":\\\"esinecan/agentic-ai-browser\\\",\\\"has_discussions\\\":false,\\\"has_downloads\\\":true,\\\"has_issues\\\":true,\\\"has_pages\\\":false,\\\"has_projects\\\":true,\\\"has_wiki\\\":true,\\\"homepage\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/esinecan/agentic-ai-browser\\\",\\\"id\\\":938957277,\\\"is_template\\\":false,\\\"language\\\":\\\"TypeScript\\\",\\\"license\\\":null,\\\"mirror_url\\\":null,\\\"name\\\":\\\"agentic-ai-browser\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"R_kgDON_dZ3Q\\\",\\\"open_issues\\\":0,\\\"open_issues_count\\\":0,\\\"owner\\\":{\\\"avatar_url\\\":\\\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/7694350?v=4\\\",\\\"html_url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/esinecan\\\",\\\"id\\\":7694350,\\\"login\\\":\\\"esinecan\\\",\\\"node_id\\\":\\\"MDQ6VXNlcjc2OTQzNTA=\\\",\\\"site_admin\\\":false,\\\"type\\\":\\\"User\\\"},\\\"permissions\\\":{\\\"admin\\\":false,\\\"maintain\\\":false,\\\"pull\\\":true,\\\"push\\\":false,\\\"triage\\\":false},\\\"private\\\":false,\\\"pushed_at\\\":\\\"2025-06-04T16:54:13Z\\\",\\\"score\\\":1,\\\"size\\\":16064,\\\"stargazers_count\\\":162,\\\"topics\\\":[],\\\"updated_at\\\":\\\"2026-04-02T22:14:07Z\\\",\\\"visibility\\\":\\\"public\\\",\\\"watchers\\\":162,\\\"watchers_count\\\":162,\\\"web_commit_signoff_required\\\":false}],\\\"total_count\\\":1660},\\\"version\\\":\\\"20260407_00\\\",\\\"auth_refresh_required\\\":false,\\\"mercury_last_http_status_code\\\":200,\\\"is_latest_version\\\":true,\\\"successful\\\":true,\\\"log_id\\\":\\\"log_vTRTlJvTXjjv\\\"}\"}],\"isError\":false},\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"id\":4}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775649145006}}
{"type":"message","id":"73939331","parentId":"8764e419","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:52:28.872Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！让我告诉用户。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n没有安装 ❌\n\n不过找到了！**agent-browser** 是 **Vercel Labs** 开发的 AI 浏览器自动化 CLI：\n\n| 项目 | ⭐ | 语言 |\n|------|---:|------|\n| **[vercel-labs/agent-browser](https://github.com/vercel-labs/agent-browser)** | 28k ⭐ | Rust |\n| [magnitudedev/browser-agent](https://github.com/magnitudedev/browser-agent) | 4k | TypeScript |\n| [browser-use/agent-sdk](https://github.com/browser-use/agent-sdk) | 656 | Python |\n\n**用途**：用自然语言让 AI 控制浏览器自动化操作（ scraping、测试、工作流等）\n\n要安装吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":62936,"output":160,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63096,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775649145019,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9ff954df-3056-4885-ab4e-8b412cbca0c6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"da9ad8cc","parentId":"73939331","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:52:46.988Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-08 19:52 GMT+8] 有什么用"}],"timestamp":1775649166979}}
{"type":"message","id":"1c5472d1","parentId":"da9ad8cc","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:53:01.090Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 agent-browser 有什么用，我用中文解释一下它的用途。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**agent-browser** = AI 控制的浏览器\n\n### 能做什么\n\n| 场景 | 示例 |\n|------|------|\n| 🌐 **网页自动化** | 帮你填表单、点按钮、滚动页面 |\n| 📥 **数据抓取** | 自动抓取网页内容（比传统爬虫更智能） |\n| 🧪 **测试** | 自动跑 web 应用的 UI 测试 |\n| 📝 **截图** | 截取网页截图 / PDF |\n| 🔄 **重复任务** | 批量处理需要手动操作的工作 |\n\n### 对比传统方式\n\n| 方式 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| 脚本/Puppeteer | 需要写代码，结构化抓取 |\n| **agent-browser** | 用自然语言描述，AI 自己理解和操作 |\n\n### 示例\n\n```bash\n# 打开网页并截图\nagent-browser \"打开 github.com 并截图\"\n\n# 抓取数据\nagent-browser \"帮我搜索最新的 AI 新闻并保存标题\"\n```\n\n相当于有个 AI \"看\"着浏览器帮你干活。要装一个试试吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5393,"output":237,"cacheRead":57728,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63358,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775649167005,"responseId":"019d6cef829b01d307d8b7cc7cf2338d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d4b91425","parentId":"1c5472d1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:55:01.314Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-08 19:55 GMT+8] 这个呢scrapling"}],"timestamp":1775649301308}}
{"type":"message","id":"b4d0bfa4","parentId":"d4b91425","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:55:14.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 scrapling 是什么，让我搜索一下。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6cf19c635aabee3e1c13f93cc471","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -X POST \"https://backend.composio.dev/v3/mcp/9dfc9342-cd7f-4c47-b705-c37cdd6b5d77/mcp?user_id=pg-test-Zbs2NXxz5sCER7mGC4PDfrHYJAjBG786\" \\\n  -H \"x-api-key: ak_UiJSwKr2LlcWQTkcR9bT\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -H \"Accept: application/json, text/event-stream\" \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"GITHUB_FIND_REPOSITORIES\",\"arguments\":{\"query\":\"scrapling in:name\",\"per_page\":10}},\"id\":5}' \\\n  --connect-timeout 10 -m 30 2>/dev/null","timeout":45}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":5550,"output":232,"cacheRead":57856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63638,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775649301325,"responseId":"019d6cf18d85d940366e77263b643c6d"}}
