{"type":"message","id":"1af91151","parentId":"e06efca1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:55:24.902Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了！Scrapling 是一个非常流行的 Python 网页爬取框架，已经有 35k+ stars。还有相关的 OpenClaw skill 可以安装。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n找到了！**Scrapling** 超火的：\n\n| 仓库 | ⭐ | 说明 |\n|------|---:|------|\n| **[D4Vinci/Scrapling](https://github.com/D4Vinci/Scrapling)** | 35k | 自适应 Web 爬取框架 |\n| [Cedriccmh/claude-code-skill-scrapling](https://github.com/Cedriccmh/claude-code-skill-scrapling) | 210 | Claude Code 的 skill |\n| [cyberchitta/scrapling-fetch-mcp](https://github.com/cyberchitta/scrapling-fetch-mcp) | 76 | MCP 服务器 |\n\n### 特点\n\n- ⚡ **自适应** - 页面结构变了能自动重新定位元素\n- 🛡️ **绕过防护** - 开箱即用绕过 Cloudflare Turnstile 等反爬\n- 🕷️ **爬虫框架** - 支持并发、多 Session、代理轮换、暂停/恢复\n- 🎯 **支持 XPath 和 AI 选择器**\n\n### 对比\n\n| 工具 | 特点 |\n|------|------|\n| **Scrapling** | 智能自适应 + 防检测 |\n| agent-browser | AI 控制浏览器，视觉优先 |\n| 传统爬虫 | 固定规则，易失效 |\n\n---\n\n你的 OpenClaw 已经有 `web_fetch` 了，但遇到 Cloudflare 保护的网站会失败。Scrapling 可以作为**替代方案**。\n\n有 OpenClaw skill 可以直接安装：`openclaw-skill-scrapling-mcp`\n\n要装吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":68128,"output":359,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68487,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775649320055,"responseId":"chatcmpl-71875226-07e3-4830-b261-f4ce11cb98c2"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5fd0be75","parentId":"1af91151","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:56:12.172Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Wed 2026-04-08 19:56 GMT+8] scrapling和agent-browser有什么区别呢？可以一起用吗"}],"timestamp":1775649372162}}
{"type":"message","id":"d33f057b","parentId":"5fd0be75","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:56:17.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问 scrapling 和 agent-browser 的区别，以及能否一起用。我来总结一下：\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 区别\n\n| | **Scrapling** | **agent-browser** |\n|---|---|---|\n| **方式** | 发送 HTTP 请求，解析 HTML | 启动真实浏览器，AI 控制操作 |\n| **速度** | ⚡ 快（毫秒级） | 🐢 慢（需要加载页面） |\n| **适用** | 结构化数据、API 难访问的页面 | 需要 JS 渲染、登录、交互的页面 |\n| **反爬** | 🛡️ 内置绕过 Cloudflare | 🛡️ 浏览器指纹更难检测 |\n| **资源** | 💰 轻量 | 💸 较重（需要浏览器） |\n\n### 一句话\n\n- **Scrapling** = 隐身的高速爬虫\n- **agent-browser** = AI 控制的真人浏览器\n\n### 可以一起用吗？\n\n✅ 可以！推荐策略：\n\n```\nScrapling（优先）\n    ↓ 失败或被拦截\nagent-browser（兜底）\n```\n\n比如：\n1. 先用 Scrapling 抓页面\n2. 遇到 Cloudflare 盾 → 切 agent-browser 截图/操作\n3. 或者 Scrapling 搞不定时，用 agent-browser 模拟人工\n\n---\n\n两个都装？还是有其他想法？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":68511,"output":280,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68791,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775649372180,"responseId":"chatcmpl-65aa2d60-f31e-4390-8570-2ce93220c610"}}
