{"type":"message","id":"243045c9","parentId":"d721a44b","timestamp":"2026-04-08T11:57:13.740Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我试试直接看 agent-browser 的 releases 或者安装方式。\n\n我现在网络受限，很难直接从 GitHub 获取信息。让我先把能做的做了：\n1. 创建 scrapling skill 基础\n2. 告诉用户 agent-browser 需要 Rust 环境\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_6150b1618ec642e3929f729a","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Scrapling Skill\n\n> 自适应 Web 爬取框架，用于绕过反爬虫保护\n\n## 安装\n\n```bash\npip install scrapling\n```\n\n## 使用\n\n```python\nfrom scrapling import Fetcher, Parser\n\n# 获取页面\nfetcher = Fetcher()\nresponse = fetcher.get(\"https://example.com\")\n\n# 解析内容\nparser = Parser(response.text)\ntitles = parser.get_text(\"h1\")\n```\n\n## MCP 服务器（可选）\n\n如需 MCP 接口：\n```bash\npip install scrapling-fetch-mcp\nscrapling-fetch-mcp\n```\n\n## 配置\n\n无默认配置，按需调整 fetcher 和 parser 参数。\n\n---\nversion: 1.0","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scrapling/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":69384,"output":236,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69620,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775649429616,"responseId":"chatcmpl-e6183fc5-2790-46aa-9d23-5d3a8089e950"}}
