{"type":"message","id":"dc1972b0","parentId":"ebbf666d","timestamp":"2026-04-08T12:23:54.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"下载失败了。网络环境有限制。\n\n让我尝试一种替代方案 - 看看是否可以使用其他工具如 playwright 或者 puppeteer 来实现类似的浏览器自动化功能。或者让用户在他们自己的环境中安装。\n\n但首先，让我尝试用一个更轻量的解决方案 - 比如通过 npm 安装的 playwright。\n\n实际上，看起来这个环境的网络连接到 GitHub 非常慢或者根本无法下载大文件。让我直接告诉用户这个情况，并为他们提供手动安装的指令。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n网络太慢，下载失败 😅\n\n换种方式 - 试试用 npm 安装 Playwright（也能做浏览器自动化）：\n\n```bash\n# 安装 playwright\nnpm install -g playwright\n\n# 安装浏览器\nnpx playwright install chromium\n```\n\n或者你在**本地 Mac** 终端直接运行：\n\n```bash\n# Mac 直接装\nbrew install agent-browser\n```\n\n你想怎么处理？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":204,"output":167,"cacheRead":78080,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78451,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775651023085,"responseId":"019d6d0bd6ebbcb007d59cdedc2b5510"}}
