{"type":"message","id":"7b80f53e","parentId":"859d51e2","timestamp":"2026-04-08T12:25:38.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问我是否用不了。确实，当前环境网络受限，下载 agent-browser 失败了。但我可以尝试用其他方式来实现浏览器自动化功能。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n是的，当前环境网络受限，下载 agent-browser 失败 ❌\n\n但我可以换种方式实现类似功能：\n\n### 方案 1：安装 Scrapling（Python）\n\n```bash\npip install scrapling\n```\n\n这个能抓取大部分网页，包括有 Cloudflare 保护的。\n\n### 方案 2：我在你的 GitHub 仓库里看到有 playwright\n\nComposio 的 GitHub 工具就可以操作仓库，不需要浏览器。\n\n### 方案 3：等你本地网络好了再装\n\n你在本地 Mac 终端跑：\n```bash\nbrew install agent-browser\n```\n\n---\n\n你本地能跑吗？或者先用 Scrapling 替代？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":77928,"output":161,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78089,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775651133780,"responseId":"chatcmpl-548e3cb2-8b6a-478c-8dab-977c3e300c3e"}}
