{"type":"message","id":"d3debb20","parentId":"0ca57763","timestamp":"2026-04-08T12:40:55.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"安装完成。现在创建一个 skill 文件帮助用户更好地使用 agent-browser。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n成功了！🎉\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6d1b38acc0a3eeead10c3245bda3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Agent Browser Skill\n\n> AI 控制的浏览器自动化工具\n\n## 安装\n\nagent-browser 已在 `~/.local/bin/agent-browser`\n\n## 使用\n\n```bash\n# 打开网页并截图\nagent-browser \"打开 github.com 并截图\"\n\n# 抓取页面内容\nagent-browser \"获取 openclaw.ai 首页的标题\"\n\n# 自动化操作\nagent-browser \"打开 Google，搜索 'Python'，并点击第一个结果\"\n\n# 填表单\nagent-browser \"填写表单：姓名=张三，邮箱=test@example.com\"\n```\n\n## 常用命令\n\n- 截图: `agent-browser \"截图\"`\n- 获取内容: `agent-browser \"获取页面文本\"`\n- 点击: `agent-browser \"点击登录按钮\"`\n- 输入: `agent-browser \"在搜索框输入 Python\"`\n\n## 浏览器管理\n\n```bash\n# 查看打开的标签页\nagent-browser \"列出所有标签页\"\n\n# 关闭浏览器\nagent-browser \"关闭浏览器\"\n```\n\n---\nversion: 1.0","path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/agent-browser/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":14593,"output":267,"cacheRead":92032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106892,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775652038871,"responseId":"019d6d1b24aca32c239a3315282f68cf"}}
