{"type":"message","id":"51e23566","parentId":"111d31c7","timestamp":"2026-04-08T13:13:59.378Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"普通 curl 会被 Cloudflare/验证码拦截。\n\n所以：\n1. curl - 简单但会被拦截\n2. Playwright - 慢但能绕过防护\n3. Scrapling - 理论上最简单，但有 bug\n\n让我给用户总结一下效率对比。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n效率对比：\n\n| 方法 | 速度 | 成功率 | 复杂度 |\n|------|------|--------|--------|\n| `curl` | ⚡ 最快 | ❌ 被拦截 | 最简单 |\n| **Playwright** | 🐢 慢 | ✅ 能抓 | 需写代码 |\n| Scrapling | ⚡ 快 | ❓ 有 bug | 最简单 |\n\n目前 **Playwright 最稳定**。我给你写个快捷脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6d398c6a8bca2fdf25b2c02f2c3b","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"简单的网页抓取工具\"\"\"\nimport sys\nfrom playwright.sync_api import sync_playwright\n\ndef fetch(url, wait=2):\n    with sync_playwright() as p:\n        browser = p.chromium.launch(headless=True)\n        page = browser.new_page()\n        page.goto(url)\n        page.wait_for_timeout(wait * 1000)\n        content = page.content()\n        title = page.title()\n        browser.close()\n        return content, title\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    url = sys.argv[1] if len(sys.argv) > 1 else \"https://example.com\"\n    content, title = fetch(url)\n    print(f\"Title: {title}\")\n    print(f\"Length: {len(content)}\")\n    print(content[:500])","path":"~/.local/bin/fetch"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":1693,"output":349,"cacheRead":116992,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119034,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775654020438,"responseId":"019d6d3969ca78b6dcfe65437fd48381"}}
