{"type":"message","id":"171041cc","parentId":"f2013b34","timestamp":"2026-04-08T16:51:35.938Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求：\n1. 先评分这个实现硬拦截层的方案\n2. 然后实现硬拦截层作为 MVP\n3. 优先使用刚刚给的代码\n\n刚才已经评过分了（4/5），现在需要实现。用户说\"优先使用刚刚给的代码\"，指的是他在消息里贴的那段 CRITICAL_PATTERNS 的 Python 代码。\n\n让我实现一个硬拦截层 MVP：\n1. 创建一个 interceptor 模块\n2. 包含 CRITICAL_PATTERNS\n3. 提供 critical_intercept 函数\n4. 可以作为一个 OpenClaw skill 或者独立模块\n\n让我先评分，然后实现。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6e01113c5565b55310be2443da75","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/critical-interceptor"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":540,"output":159,"cacheRead":132736,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":133435,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775667083468,"responseId":"019d6e00e92690730376cf51ecff8dfd"}}
