{"type":"message","id":"119f1977","parentId":"c87d36d8","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:00:32.924Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了。路由器有 intentDetector（意图检测），但没有独立的评分 API。意图检测返回 isTask: true/false，但没有详细的复杂度评分。\n\n让我检查 intentDetector 的完整功能。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d477f4d100ce47329ec407c3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js","limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":49135,"output":83,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49218,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775667631294,"responseId":"chatcmpl-9358619f-634e-48ff-81a9-fc7706fd6224"}}
{"type":"message","id":"976ad8dc","parentId":"119f1977","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:00:32.996Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d477f4d100ce47329ec407c3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// intentDetector.js\n// 同步轻量级意图判断 + 异步增强\n\nconst axios = require('axios');\n\n// 规则配置\nconst RULE = {\n actionVerbs: /(写|做|执行|运行|处理|分析|检查|修复|重构|生成|编译|部署|创建|修改|删除|帮我|请|麻烦)/i,\n questionWords: /(吗|？|能不能|可不可以|是否|什么|为什么|怎么|如何)/i,\n confirmWords: /^(是|好|做|继续|可以|行|嗯|ok|yes)$/i,\n taskContinuation: /(再|又|也|还|继续|接着)/i\n};\n\n// 同步规则打分（快速，不依赖外部）\nfunction ruleBasedScore(message) {\n let score = 0;\n if (RULE.actionVerbs.test(message)) score += 2;\n if (RULE.confirmWords.test(message)) score += 1;\n if (RULE.taskContinuation.test(message)) score += 1;\n if (RULE.questionWords.test(message)) score -= 2;\n return score;\n}\n\n// 异步上下文增强（获取最近对话，调用 Context API）\nasync function contextEnhance(message, convId, timeoutMs = 500) {\n if (!convId) return 0;\n try {\n const controller = new AbortController();\n const timeout = setTimeout(() => controller.abort(), timeoutMs);\n const res = await axios.get(`http://localhost:3101/api/context/history`, {\n params: { convId, limit: 3 },\n signal: controller.signal\n });\n clearTimeout(timeout);\n const history = res.data.messages || [];\n let bonus = 0;\n const lastAssistant = history[history.length - 1]?.content || '';\n if (/要不要|是否|可以执行|需要我帮你/i.test(lastAssistant)) bonus += 1;\n if (RULE.confirmWords.test(message) && bonus > 0) bonus += 1;\n return bonus;\n } catch (err) {\n return 0;\n }\n}\n\n// 异步记忆增强（查询相似任务）\nasync function memoryEnhance(message, memoryStore, timeoutMs = 300) {\n if (!memoryStore || typeof memoryStore.query !== 'function') return 0;\n try {\n const controller = new AbortController();\n\n[34 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775667632989}}
{"type":"message","id":"1ebce349","parentId":"976ad8dc","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:00:36.910Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我明白了。路由器只有意图检测（intentDetector），用于判断是否是任务，但没有任务复杂度评分（score）API。\n\nSOUL.md 中提到的评分机制（/api/score）目前**没有实现**。只有意图判断功能可用（/api/intent）。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 问题找到了\n\n路由器 **3102 端口** 正在运行，但：\n\n| API | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| `/api/intent` | ✅ 可用（意图判断） |\n| `/api/score` | ❌ **未实现** |\n\n---\n\n### 当前可用功能\n\n**intentDetector.js** 只做了意图判断：\n\n```javascript\n// 规则打分\nactionVerbs (写/做/执行/运行...) → +2\nconfirmWords (好/可以/行...) → +1  \nquestionWords (吗/怎么/如何...) → -2\n```\n\n返回 `isTask: true/false`，但**没有复杂度评分**。\n\n---\n\n### 结论\n\n**评分机制（`/api/score`）未实现**。需要：\n\n1. 新建 `taskScorer.js` 模块\n2. 实现多维度评分逻辑\n3. 挂载到路由器\n\n要我现在实现评分模块吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":49723,"output":253,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49976,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775667632998,"responseId":"chatcmpl-1b55e7ba-471e-4e48-8ed6-c9a0b398211b"}}
