{"type":"message","id":"e12639b6","parentId":"87f05cf1","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:04:04.339Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问评分因子是什么。让我回顾一下之前在 AGENTS.md 里定义的评分因子。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d6e0c672564c597cb431d0728e3c2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":50811,"output":55,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52018,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775667836455,"responseId":"019d6e0c4f7a9ef7035f5486e2ddf7fd"}}
{"type":"message","id":"94711e07","parentId":"e12639b6","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:04:04.402Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d6e0c672564c597cb431d0728e3c2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OpenClaw Workspace\n\nThis is the workspace for OpenClaw AI assistant.\n\n## 核心规则\n\n### 任务执行前必做：意图判断 + 复杂度评估\n\n**第一步：意图判断** (`POST /api/intent`)\n- 判断用户消息是否是任务\n- 动作词（写、做、执行、创建、帮我等）→ +2分\n- 疑问词（吗、怎么、如何等）→ -2分\n- 确认词（好、行、可以等）→ +1分\n- 置信度 > 0.5 时触发评分\n\n**第二步：复杂度评分** (`GET /api/score`)\n收到任何任务请求时，**必须先使用 task_orchestrator 进行自动评分**，再根据分数选择执行策略：\n\n| 总分 | 执行方式 | 超时 | 内存限制 |\n|------|----------|------|----------|\n| ≤20 | DIRECT | 30s | - |\n| 21-40 | STEP_ARCHIVE | 60s | 1024MB |\n| 41-60 | SPAWN_SUBAGENT | 60-180s | 2048MB |\n| 61-80 | PARALLEL_SHARDS | 120-160s | 2048MB |\n| >80 | MEGA_TASK | 7200s | 8192MB |\n\n评分因子：\n- 指令数量 (instructionCount)\n- 代码行数 (codeLines)\n- 依赖复杂度 (dependencyComplexity)\n- CPU 强度 (cpuIntensity)\n- IO 强度 (ioIntensity)\n- 网络强度 (networkIntensity)\n- 预估执行时间 (estimatedDuration)\n- 规模指数 (scaleIndex)\n\n### 子代理进度上报 (v2.0)\n\nspawn 子代理时复用进度上报机制：\n- 子代理输出 `[PROGRESS] <percent>% | <step>/<total> | <description>` 格式\n- 主代理捕获 stdout 解析进度标记，限流转发给用户 (1条/秒)\n- 心跳：30秒无输出发送\"仍在运行\"\n- 无产出检测：30秒无输出 → 警告 → 强制终止\n- 相关配置：SUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB, PROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS 等\n\n### 任务编排器 (task_orchestrator v3.0)\n\n整合三大能力：\n1. **任务评分路由**: 多维度评分 → DIRECT/STEP_ARCHIVE/SPAWN_SUBAGENT/PARALLEL_SHARDS/MEGA_TASK\n2. **上下文保护**: 消息数≥50 或 字符≥100KB 或 token≥80% → 自动压缩写入记忆\n3. **子代理进度上报**: 同上 v2.0\n\n技能文件: \n- `~/.openclaw/skills/task_orchestrator/` (核心代码)\n- `~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/` (工作区副本)\n\n中间件:\n- Router: `localhost:3102` (任务评分 + 反向代理)\n- Context API: `localhost:3101` (上下文管理)\n\n### 环境变量\n\n```\nOPENCLAW_GATEWAY=http://127.0.0.1:18789\nROUTER_PORT=3102\nSUBAGENT_MEMORY_LIMIT_MB=2048\nPROGRESS_MIN_INTERVAL_MS=1000\n```\n\n---"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775667844396}}
{"type":"message","id":"34f5536f","parentId":"94711e07","timestamp":"2026-04-08T17:04:09.051Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是评分因子，AGENTS.md 里定义了 8 个评分因子，我已经在 scoring.js 里实现了这些。让我给用户列出当前的评分因子。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 当前评分因子 (8个)\n\n| 因子 | 权重 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **instructionCount** | 12% | 指令数量（用 `&&` `;` `\\n` 计数） |\n| **codeLines** | 8% | 代码行数 |\n| **dependencyComplexity** | 10% | 依赖复杂度（npm/pip install → 4） |\n| **cpuIntensity** | 10% | CPU 强度（compile/build → 4） |\n| **ioIntensity** | 8% | IO 强度（cp/mv/tar/dd → 4） |\n| **networkIntensity** | 12% | 网络强度（curl/wget/git clone → 4） |\n| **estimatedDuration** | 12% | 预估执行时间（sleep/compile → 4） |\n| **scaleIndex** | 28% | 规模指数（docker/terraform/k8s → 加分） |\n\n---\n\n权重加起来 100%，每个因子 1-5 分，最终换算成 0-100 分。\n\n这些因子在 `scoring.js` 里已实现 ✅\n\n要调整权重或因子吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":52700,"output":284,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":52984,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775667844404,"responseId":"chatcmpl-060771c0-57a6-4525-93b1-0df9080eb899"}}
