{"type":"message","id":"38ff9197","parentId":"21b51e20","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:58:50.274Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在问什么 API 服务。之前我提到可以启动 FastAPI 服务来接收 HTTP 请求。让我解释一下可以做什么。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n可以启动一个 **HTTP API 服务**，让我能通过 HTTP 调用场景分类器：\n\n```bash\n# 启动服务后，可以这样调用：\ncurl -X POST \"http://localhost:8080/classify\" -d '{\"text\": \"帮我分析代码质量\"}'\n```\n\n返回：\n```json\n{\n  \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.48,\n  \"response\": \"【任务提交模板】任务已提交...\"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 可以做什么\n\n| 能力 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **自动分类** | 收到用户消息自动识别场景 |\n| **风险拦截** | CRITICAL 请求直接拒绝 |\n| **模板回复** | 根据场景返回标准化回复 |\n| **接入 LLM** | 对接真实 LLM 生成最终回复 |\n| **反馈收集** | 记录误分类用于优化 |\n\n---\n\n要启动吗？启动后会监听 `localhost:8080`。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":904,"output":219,"cacheRead":71552,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72675,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775707118079,"responseId":"019d70644f09fa3c190a049c909c4dab"}}
