{"type":"message","id":"8c97a849","parentId":"a6edc69a","timestamp":"2026-04-09T03:59:40.330Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户想要启动 API 服务，并且问能不能监听网页。这里的\"网页\"可能是指：\n\n1. 通过网页浏览器访问服务\n2. 还是想通过 HTTP 接口被外部调用\n\n让我启动一个简单的 FastAPI 服务，同时支持：\n1. HTTP API 调用（curl）\n2. 也可以在浏览器中打开\n\n实际上这里的\"监听网页\"可能是指能不能让外部访问，但当前在 VPS 上，没有公网域名，只能本地访问。\n\n让我先启动服务，然后解释清楚。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7065362410958dbfd9706c05cae3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"pip install fastapi uvicorn -q","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":4106,"output":137,"cacheRead":68608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72851,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775707168968,"responseId":"019d70651568e23b43f25a4e453a3560"}}
