{"type":"message","id":"2068048e","parentId":"74d8cc23","timestamp":"2026-04-09T04:50:38.477Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！成功了。现在用户可以通过 localhost:3102 访问场景分类器。让我告诉用户这个好消息。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**现在可以了！** 🎉\n\n通过 `localhost:3102` 访问：\n\n```bash\n# 分类\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/classify \\\n  -d '{\"text\": \"帮我分析代码质量\"}'\n\n# 返回\n{\n  \"response\": \"【任务提交模板】...\",\n  \"scene\": \"task_multi_step\",\n  \"confidence\": 0.48,\n  \"intercepted\": false\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 已集成到 3102 路由器\n\n| 端点 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| `GET /health` | 健康检查 |\n| `GET /api/score?task=...` | 任务评分 |\n| `POST /api/intent` | 意图判断 |\n| `POST /api/classify` | 场景分类 (新) |\n| `POST /api/task` | 任务创建 |"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":76206,"output":211,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77569,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775710223693,"responseId":"019d7093b0f85e73184ea8159de484ca"}}
