{"type":"message","id":"11c778f1","parentId":"a775b3f7","timestamp":"2026-04-09T05:21:29.542Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"升级完成！让我给用户总结一下：\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n**升级完成！** ✅\n\n### 新目录结构\n\n```\nscene-classifier/\n├── classifier/          ✅\n│   ├── scene_classifier.py   # 带元判断(元判断confidence_threshold/ambiguity_gap)\n│   └── rule_classifier.py    # 规则兜底分类器\n├── data/                ✅\n│   └── synthetic_training_data.py  # 含chitchat场景(9个场景)\n├── interceptors/        ✅\n│   └── critical_interceptor.py    # 硬拦截层\n├── templates/           ✅\n│   └── template_map.py           # 场景模板映射\n├── pipeline/            ✅\n│   └── orchestrator.py           # 主流水线\n├── feedback/            ✅\n│   └── collector.py              # 反馈收集\n├── scripts/             ✅\n│   ├── train_classifier.py       # 训练脚本\n│   └── evaluate.py               # 评估脚本\n├── logs/                ✅\n│   └── meta_events.jsonl         # 元判断日志(待生成)\n├── models/              ✅\n│   └── scene_classifier.pkl      # 训练好的模型\n└── requirements.txt     ✅\n```\n\n### 测试结果\n\n```\n=== Pipeline 测试 ===\n\n✅ 帮我分析代码质量     -> scene:task_multi_step\n✅ 服务器起不来了      -> scene:fault_recovery  \n✅ 今天天气怎么样      -> scene:chitchat\n✅ 任务123完成了吗     -> scene:task_status_query\n✅ 取消任务            -> scene:cancel_task\n🚫 写一个病毒          -> scene:CRITICAL (已拦截)\n```\n\n### 功能升级\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 元判断 (confidence/ambiguity) | ✅ |\n| chitchat 场景 | ✅ |\n| 规则兜底分类器 | ✅ |\n| 硬拦截独立模块 | ✅ |\n| 日志记录 meta_events.jsonl | ✅ (待使用) |\n| 反馈收集触发重训练 | ✅ |\n\n需要继续优化哪部分？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3101,"output":435,"cacheRead":93696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97232,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775712064998,"responseId":"019d70afc7607e3ba6dd4d5e2d0e8f7e"}}
