{"type":"message","id":"ff29a8c1","parentId":"91099e87","timestamp":"2026-04-09T05:43:41.882Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_89fcce0836564a7c8a4d64d7","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// 对话路径拦截 - 意图判断 + 任务评分\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res, next) => {\n  const userMessage = req.body.message || req.body.text || req.body.content;\n  if (!userMessage) return next();\n  \n  const convId = req.body.conversationId || req.body.sessionId;\n  const memoryStore = global.vectorMemory || null;\n  \n  // 同步快速判断\n  const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage, convId, memoryStore);\n  \n  if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n    // 触发任务评分\n    const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n    const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n    console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n    // 记录指标\n    metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n    metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n    healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n    req.body.taskRouting = plan;\n  }\n  \n  next();\n});\n\n// 代理到 Gateway（同时支持HTTP和WebSocket）\nconst proxy = createProxyMiddleware({\n  target: GATEWAY_URL,\n  changeOrigin: true,\n\n[62 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775713421876}}
{"type":"message","id":"fdedd301","parentId":"ff29a8c1","timestamp":"2026-04-09T05:43:49.262Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我明白了。让我给用户解释当前的情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 当前自动调用情况\n\n**入口**: `/api/chat/send` (发送消息)\n\n```\n用户消息 → /api/chat/send\n              │\n              ├── 意图判断 (isTask + confidence)\n              │     ↓\n              │   如果 isTask=true 且 confidence>0.5\n              │     ↓\n              └── 评分 (score + plan)\n                    ↓\n                  转发到 Gateway 执行\n```\n\n---\n\n### 自动调用逻辑\n\n| 步骤 | 条件 | 是否自动调用 |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| **意图判断** | 每次发消息 | ✅ 自动 |\n| **评分** | isTask=true 且 confidence>0.5 | ✅ 自动 |\n| **场景分类** | 需要手动调用 `/api/classify` | ❌ **不会自动** |\n\n---\n\n### 当前情况\n\n```javascript\n// chat/send 里自动调用了：\n- detectIntent()    // 意图判断 ✅\n- computeFineScore() // 评分 ✅ (满足条件时)\n\n// 没有自动调用：\n- classify()        // 场景分类 ❌\n```\n\n---\n\n### 分类目前需要手动调用\n\n```bash\n# 手动调用分类\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/classify \\\n  -d '{\"text\": \"帮我分析代码\"}'\n\n# 或者 8080 端口\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:8080/classify \\\n  -d '{\"text\": \"帮我分析代码\"}'\n```\n\n---\n\n### 如果要自动调用\n\n需要在 `/api/chat/send` 里加上分类调用：\n\n```javascript\n// 当前逻辑\nif (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n  score = await computeFineScore(userMessage); // 评分\n}\n\n// 可选：加上分类\nif (isTask) {\n  scene = await axios.post(`${SCENE_CLASSIFIER_URL}/classify`, {text: userMessage});\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n需要我加上**自动分类**吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":109244,"output":417,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775713421888,"responseId":"chatcmpl-43f1179b-8d86-490b-a2fa-cab2ca105a67"}}
