{"type":"message","id":"53f20288","parentId":"98ab2bd2","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:05:43.077Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d70d88e9883a22c00552222893a4e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"taskSpec\":\"实现评分自动+分类自动+评分分类联动：在OpenClaw路由器中嵌入handleChatSend函数，实现用户发消息时自动意图判断+自动评分+自动场景分类，并支持评分后自动触发分类的联动逻辑\",\"score\":20,\"routing\":{\"mode\":\"DIRECT\",\"timeoutSec\":30,\"memLimitMB\":null},\"factors\":{\"instructionCount\":1,\"codeLines\":1,\"dependencyComplexity\":1,\"cpuIntensity\":1,\"ioIntensity\":1,\"networkIntensity\":1,\"estimatedDuration\":1,\"scaleIndex\":1},\"message\":\"Task scored, ready to execute\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"{\"taskSpec\":\"实现评分自动+分类自动+评分分类联动：在OpenClaw路由器中嵌入handleChatSend函数，实现用户发消息时自动意图判断+自动评分+自动场景分类，并支持评分后自动触发分类的联动逻辑\",\"score\":20,\"routing\":{\"mode\":\"DIRECT\",\"timeoutSec\":30,\"memLimitMB\":null},\"factors\":{\"instructionCount\":1,\"codeLines\":1,\"dependencyComplexity\":1,\"cpuIntensity\":1,\"ioIntensity\":1,\"networkIntensity\":1,\"estimatedDuration\":1,\"scaleIndex\":1},\"message\":\"Task scored, ready to execute\"}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775714743071}}
{"type":"message","id":"e92bf2e7","parentId":"53f20288","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:05:59.123Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"评分结果：总分20，执行模式DIRECT，超时30秒。现在回答如何实现。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 评分结果\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **总分** | **20** |\n| **执行模式** | **DIRECT** (直接执行) |\n| **超时** | 30s |\n\n---\n\n## 实现方案\n\n### 目标\n\n1. **评分自动** - 用户发消息时自动触发评分\n2. **分类自动** - 用户发消息时自动触发分类\n3. **评分+分类联动** - 评分后根据结果自动触发分类\n\n---\n\n### 怎么做\n\n#### 步骤1：在现有路由器 `/api/chat/send` 基础上改造\n\n```javascript\n// 现有流程\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res, next) => {\n  // 只有意图判断 + 条件评分\n  const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n  if (isTask && confidence > 0.5) {\n    const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage); // 评分\n  }\n  next(); // 转发到 Gateway\n});\n```\n\n#### 步骤2：加入分类 + 联动逻辑\n\n```javascript\napp.post('/api/chat/send', async (req, res) => {\n  const userMessage = req.body.message;\n  const convId = req.body.conversationId;\n  \n  // 1. 硬拦截 (CRITICAL 直接返回)\n  const blocked = criticalIntercept(userMessage);\n  if (blocked) {\n    return res.json({ reply: blocked, blocked: true });\n  }\n  \n  // 2. 意图判断 (必做)\n  const intent = await detectIntent(userMessage, convId);\n  \n  // 3. 评分 (如果是任务)\n  let scoreResult = null;\n  if (intent.isTask && intent.confidence > 0.5) {\n    scoreResult = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n    // 记录评分结果\n    req.body.taskRouting = scoreResult.plan;\n  }\n  \n  // 4. 分类 (联动触发)\n  let classifyResult = null;\n  // 联动规则：任务类型 或 意图不明确时 触发分类\n  if (intent.isTask || scoreResult?.score > 20) {\n    classifyResult = await axios.post(`http://localhost:5000/classify`, { text: userMessage });\n  }\n  \n  // 5. 构造响应 (注入评分+分类结果)\n  const response = {\n    reply: \"...\", // LLM 生成\n    intent: intent,\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: classifyResult?.label,\n    meta: classifyResult?.meta\n  };\n  \n  res.json(response);\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### 思考 🤔\n\n| 问题 | 思考 |\n|------|------|\n| **性能影响** | 每条消息增加 2 次 API 调用（intent + classify），会增加 50-100ms 延迟 |\n| **评分和分类顺序** | 先评分再分类？还是并行？推荐：**先意图判断，再评分+分类并行** |\n| **结果存哪** | 评分+分类结果需要写入 context，供后续 LLM 调用使用 |\n| **分类服务依赖** | 如果 Python 分类服务挂了，是否需要同步等待降级？推荐：**超时保护** |\n| **与 Gateway 冲突** | 当前 chat/send 会转发到 Gateway，加上分类逻辑后是否需要阻止转发？ |\n\n---\n\n### 推荐联动逻辑\n\n```javascript\n// 推荐：意图判断 + 评分/分类并行\nconst intent = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n\nif (intent.isTask) {\n  // 意图明确是任务 → 评分 + 分类并行\n  const [scoreResult, classifyResult] = await Promise.all([\n    computeFineScore(userMessage),\n    classify(userMessage)  // 分类服务\n  ]);\n} else if (intent.confidence > 0.3) {\n  // 意图不确定但可能有任务 → 只分类\n  const classifyResult = await classify(userMessage);\n}\n// 否则不评分不分类\n```\n\n---\n\n**这样做可以吗？** 还是你有其他想法？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":122411,"output":864,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":123275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775714743082,"responseId":"chatcmpl-8ba84ac4-0bae-494f-83b5-948ddd2882d6"}}
