{"type":"compaction","id":"ad6643c0","parentId":"2dacec26","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:37:41.707Z","summary":"\n\n## Summary\n\n**Conversation 3 - April 9, 2026**\n\n### Goal\nBuild OpenClaw's scene classifier system with multi-layer architecture (system layer + model layer) as defined in SOUL.md v9.4\n\n### Progress\n\n### Done\n- [x] Scene classifier system fully operational with 9 scenes\n- [x] Critical-interceptor with 6 CRITICAL patterns\n- [x] API services running (8080 and 3102)\n- [x] Log file generation working (meta_events.jsonl)\n- [x] Meta-judgment mechanism (confidence_threshold=0.5, ambiguity_gap=0.1)\n- [x] Tested interaction between scoring API and classification API\n- [x] Verified no conflict between /api/score and /api/classify\n\n### In Progress\n- [ ] None - system fully operational\n\n### Blocked\n- None\n\n### Key Decisions\n- **No conflict between scoring and classification**: Tested with user input \"先评分\" (score first), confirming:\n  - `/api/intent` returns `isTask=false, confidence=0` for \"先评分\"\n  - `/api/task` returns `score=20, mode=DIRECT` for \"先评分\"\n  - `/api/classify` runs independently and returns scene=clarify\n  - Both APIs are independent and can run in parallel or sequence\n- **Score-then-classify workflow**: When user asks to score first, then execute, the system can optionally chain: score → classify (for confidence > 30)\n\n### Next Steps\n- User may want to implement score-classify联动 (score-classification chaining) as optional enhancement\n\n### Critical Context\n- Router runs on localhost:3102\n- Scene classifier API runs on localhost:8080\n- Model at: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/models/scene_classifier.pkl\n- Logs at: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/logs/meta_events.jsonl\n\n### Exact identifiers\n- Router port: 3102\n- API port: 8080\n- Scene classifier model: scene_classifier.pkl\n- Log file: logs/meta_events.jsonl\n- Confidence threshold: 0.5\n- Ambiguity gap: 0.1\n- Test input: \"先评分\"\n- /api/intent result for \"先评分\": {\"isTask\":false,\"confidence\":0}\n- /api/task result for \"先评分\": {\"taskSpec\":\"先评分\",\"score\":20,\"routing\":{\"mode\":\"DIRECT\",\"timeoutSec\":30,\"memLimitMB\":null},\"factors\":{\"instructionCount\":1,\"codeLines\":1,\"dependencyComplexity\":1,\"cpuIntensity\":1,\"ioIntensity\":1,\"networkIntensity\":1,\"estimatedDuration\":1,\"scaleIndex\":1},\"message\":\"Task scored, ready to execute\"}\n\n---\n\n## Decisions\n- 评分和分类是独立的 API，不会冲突 - 已通过测试验证 \"先评分\" 输入不会触发场景分类冲突\n- 用户可以先调用 /api/score 评分，再调用 /api/classify 分类，两者可独立运行\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 无 - 系统核心功能已完成\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- 保留所有原有系统和配置不变\n- 只在现有框架内进行测试和验证\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 用户询问是否可以实现 \"评分后自动分类\" 的联动机制 (score > 30 时自动触发 classify)\n- 用户问：\"如果我先说让你评分，你还会触发什么？会不会有什么进行冲突\"\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- 日志位置: ~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/logs/meta_events.jsonl\n- 完整路径: /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/logs/meta_events.jsonl\n- 路由器端口: 3102\n- API 端口: 8080\n- 场景分类模型: scene_classifier.pkl\n- 日志文件: logs/meta_events.jsonl\n- 置信度阈值: 0.5\n- 模糊度阈值 (ambiguity_gap): 0.1\n- 测试输入: 先评分\n- /api/intent 结果: {\"isTask\":false,\"confidence\":0}\n- /api/task 结果 (评分): score=20, mode=DIRECT\n- /api/classify 结果 (场景分类): scene=clarify (元判断触发)\n\n**Turn Context (split turn):**\n\n\n\n## Decisions\n- (无)\n\n## Open TODOs\n- 需要向用户说明评分和分类的自动调用逻辑\n\n## Constraints/Rules\n- (无)\n\n## Pending user asks\n- 用户询问：评分和分类会按照他的信息来自动调用吗？\n\n## Exact identifiers\n- 文件路径: /home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js\n- API端点: /api/score (GET, 第44行), /api/intent (POST, 第75行), /api/classify (POST, 第83行), /api/chat/send (POST, 第101行)\n- 函数名: computeFineScore, detectIntent, getExecutionPlan, getCachedScore\n- 意图检测阈值: confidence > 0.5\n- 标签/ID: openclaw-control-ui\n\n## Recent turns preserved verbatim\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 13:39 GMT+8] 如果实现评分后自动分类，优缺点是什么？代价是什么？\n- Assistant: ### 评分后自动分类 - 优缺点分析\n\n---\n\n### ✅ 优点\n\n| 优点 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **用户体验更好** | 一次请求同时获得评分+分类，无需多次调用 |\n| **减少网络开销** | 减少 1 次 HTTP 调用 |\n| **智能路由** | 可以根据分类结果自动选择执行策略（如 HIGH 风险走特殊流程） |\n| **统一入口** | 简化前端调用逻辑 |\n\n---\n\n### ❌ 缺点\n\n| 缺点 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **响应变慢** | 分类器需要加载模型（约 2-3 秒首次加载） |\n| **资源占用** | 同时占用评分+分类资源 |\n| **耦合度增加** | 两个模块强绑定，一个出问题影响全局 |\n| **灵活性下降** | 想单独评分或单独分类时反而麻烦 |\n\n---\n\n### 💰 代价\n\n| 代价 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **时间** | 首次分类 ~3 秒（模型加载），后续 ~100ms |\n| **内存** | 分类器模型占用 ~200MB |\n| **复杂性** | 需要修改路由器代码，添加联动逻辑 |\n| **维护** | 两个模块更新可能互相影响 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔧 方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 复杂度 | 性能 | 灵活性 |\n|------...\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 13:40 GMT+8] 分类是怎么个分类法\n- Assistant: ### 场景分类器工作原理\n\n---\n\n#### 1. 两层分类\n\n```\n用户输入\n   │\n   ▼\n┌─────────────────────┐\n│  1. 硬拦截层         │  ← CRITICAL 风险直接拦截\n│  critical_intercept │\n└─────────────────────┘\n   │ 通过\n   ▼\n┌─────────────────────┐\n│  2. 分类器          │\n│  (嵌入向量 + KNN)   │\n└─────────────────────┘\n   │\n   ▼\n9种场景标签\n```\n\n---\n\n#### 2. 分类器流程\n\n```\n输入: \"帮我分析代码质量\"\n   │\n   ▼\n┌────────────────────────┐\n│ Sentence-BERT 编码     │  (转为 384 维向量)\n│ paraphrase-multilingual│\n│ -MiniLM-L12-v2        │\n└────────────────────────┘\n   │\n   ▼ [0.8, 0.3, 0.2...] (向量)\n   │\n   ▼\n┌────────────────────────┐\n│  KNN 最近邻搜索        │  (找最相似的训练样本)\n│  top-3  ...\n- User: Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 13:42 GMT+8] 分类和评分的区别\n- Assistant: ### 评分 vs 分类 - 区别\n\n---\n\n| 维度 | 评分 (Score) | 分类 (Classify) |\n|------|-------------|-----------------|\n| **目的** | 判断任务复杂度 | 识别用户意图 |\n| **输出** | 0-100 分 + 执行策略 | 9种场景标签 |\n| **依据** | 代码行数、依赖、规模等 | 语义匹配、嵌入向量 |\n| **用途** | 选择执行方式 (DIRECT/MEGA_TASK) | 选择回复模板 |\n\n---\n\n### 比喻\n\n| | 评分 | 分类 |\n|--|------|------|\n| **像** | 高考阅卷打分 | 邮政分拣包裹 |\n| **判断** | 这道题答得好不好 (多少分) | 这是什么类型的包裹 |\n| **结果** | 分高/分低 → 怎么处理 | 是信件/报纸/包裹 → 怎么投递 |\n\n---\n\n### 具体例子\n\n**用户输入**: \"帮我分析这个项目的代码质量\"\n\n| 项目 | 评分 | 分类 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **输出** | score=31, mode=STEP_ARCHIVE | scene=task_multi_step |\n| **含义** | 需要分步执行，60秒超时 | 多步骤任务，用任务提交模板...\n\n## Tool Failures\n- exec: Aborted\n\n<read-files>\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\n/home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js\n~/.openclaw/workspace/config/mcporter.json\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scrapling/SKILL.md\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orchestrator/scoring.js\n~/openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md\n~/openclaw/workspace/config/mcporter.json\n\n</read-files>\n\n<modified-files>\n/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/SKILLS.md\n/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js\n~/.local/bin/fetch\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/critical-interceptor/SKILL.md\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/critical-interceptor/critical_interceptor.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/SKILL.md\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/__init__.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/api_server.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/classifier/rule_classifier.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/classifier/scene_classifier.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/data/synthetic_training_data.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/feedback/collector.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/interceptors/critical_interceptor.py\n~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scene-classifier/pipeline.py\n...and 6 more\n\n</modified-files>","firstKeptEntryId":"fdedd301","tokensBefore":134630,"details":{"readFiles":["/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/AGENTS.md","/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md","/home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js","~/.openclaw/workspace/config/mcporter.json","~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/scrapling/SKILL.md","~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/task_orc