{"type":"message","id":"cb3828e6","parentId":"94740855","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:46:12.924Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d70fcf3354b7d0d43a8a2c207a648","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    req.body.sceneMeta = sceneResult.meta;\n  }\n  \n  // 3. 记录元判断日志\n  logMeta({\n    userMessage: userMessage.slice(0, 200),\n    intent: { isTask, confidence },\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: sceneResult\n  });\n  \n  // 返回初步结果 (不等待 LLM)\n  // 将结果存入 res.locals 供后续使用\n  res.locals.intentResult = { isTask, confidence };\n  res.locals.scoreResult = scoreResult;\n  res.locals.sceneResult = sceneResult;\n  \n  // 继续转发到 Gateway\n  next();\n});\n\n// 代理到 Gateway（同时支持HTTP和WebSocket）\nconst proxy = createProxyMiddleware({\n  target: GATEWAY_URL,\n  changeOrigin: true,\n  ws: true, // 支持WebSocket\n  filter: function(req) {\n    // 不代理 /api 开头的请求，让 Express 处理\n    return !req.url.startsWith('/api');\n  },\n\n[61 more lines in file. Use offset=190 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775717172915}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa45d9cb","parentId":"cb3828e6","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:46:27.787Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到了问题：\n1. chat/send 处理函数调用了 next()，将请求转发到代理\n2. 代理配置了 filter: !req.url.startsWith('/api')\n3. 但是 chat/send 的 URL 是 /api/chat/send，所以不会被代理\n4. 然后 next() 之后，没有其他处理器了，所以返回 404\n\n解决方案：chat/send 处理完后不应该调用 next()，而应该直接返回响应（因为我们已经处理完分类和评分了）。或者只转发到 Gateway，不经过代理。\n\n让我修改一下，不要调用 next()，而是直接返回结果。或者，我们可以把 chat/send 的 URL 改一下，不以 /api 开头。\n\n实际上，chat/send 需要调用 Gateway 来执行真正的 LLM 请求。所以应该转发请求，但不应该走代理，而是直接转发到 Gateway URL。\n\n让我修改一下逻辑。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 问题发现\n\n`chat/send` 处理完评分和分类后调用 `next()`，但请求没有被正确转发。\n\n**修复**：不调用 next()，直接转发到 Gateway：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1f235f14f25c4859a1b78b0f","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"  // 3. 记录元判断日志\n  logMeta({\n    userMessage: userMessage.slice(0, 200),\n    intent: { isTask, confidence },\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: sceneResult\n  });\n  \n  // 转发到 Gateway（不走代理，直接发请求）\n  const gatewayUrl = 'http://127.0.0.1:3108' + req.originalUrl;\n  try {\n    const gatewayResponse = await axios.post(gatewayUrl, req.body, {\n      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n      timeout: 30000\n    });\n    // 合并结果\n    res.json({\n      ...gatewayResponse.data,\n      _meta: {\n        intent: { isTask, confidence },\n        score: scoreResult,\n        scene: sceneResult\n      }\n    });\n  } catch (err) {\n    console.error(`[Router] Gateway转发失败: ${err.message}`);\n    res.status(502).json({ error: 'Gateway unavailable', details: err.message });\n  }\n});","oldText":"  // 3. 记录元判断日志\n  logMeta({\n    userMessage: userMessage.slice(0, 200),\n    intent: { isTask, confidence },\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: sceneResult\n  });\n  \n  // 返回初步结果 (不等待 LLM)\n  // 将结果存入 res.locals 供后续使用\n  res.locals.intentResult = { isTask, confidence };\n  res.locals.scoreResult = scoreResult;\n  res.locals.sceneResult = sceneResult;\n  \n  // 继续转发到 Gateway\n  next();\n});"}],"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":53026,"output":663,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53689,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775717172927,"responseId":"chatcmpl-49c2a687-e1be-4237-91f2-dcb739857bab"}}
