{"type":"message","id":"1f9e750e","parentId":"0427cff1","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:47:21.002Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我可以看到：1. 路由器运行成功\n2. 意图判断成功：isTask=false, confidence=0 (对于\"测试\"这个消息)\n3. 但是 Gateway 返回404问题是 Gateway (3108) 没有 /chat/send 这个端点。让我检查一下 Gateway 的 API。可能是 URL 不对。让我看看 Gateway 实际支持什么端点，或者我应该把请求转发到正确的路径。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n[PROGRESS] 88% | 7/8 | 修复转发逻辑\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cdc4503b8e3c4935a228389d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 Gateway 支持的端点 ===\" && \\\ncurl -s http://localhost:3108/health 2>&1 | head -c 200\n\necho \"\" && echo \"=== 检查 Gateway 根路径 ===\" && \\\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3108/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\":\"测试\"}' 2>&1 | head -c 300","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":55792,"output":228,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56020,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775717235771,"responseId":"chatcmpl-40dfd271-1983-4455-9209-82911af275ed"}}
