{"type":"message","id":"fa8f2fb5","parentId":"c467fe7d","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:47:24.050Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 没有 /chat/send 端点。让我看看 Gateway 支持什么。让我试试其他端点或者直接发送消息给Gateway，看看它是如何处理聊天的。\n\nOpenClaw 的 Gateway 可能没有直接暴露 chat/send 端点，它可能通过不同的方式处理聊天。让我看看 Gateway 是怎么处理聊天消息的。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_27fd4065ccc0482082fa8065","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 检查 Gateway 的路由 ===\" && \\\ncurl -s http://localhost:3108/ 2>&1 | head -c 100\n\necho \"\" && echo \"=== 检查 openclaw-listener ===\" && \\\nps aux | grep openclaw-listener | head -3","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":56064,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56223,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775717241120,"responseId":"chatcmpl-cc240f6a-03c8-4281-8215-e7bd12a2fb2b"}}
