{"type":"message","id":"ba29898a","parentId":"bd8439e1","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:48:20.311Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Gateway 有一个Web界面，不是一个API服务。看起来OpenClaw的架构是不同的：\n\n- Router (3102): API入口，处理意图判断、评分、分类- Gateway (3108): Web UI，处理实际的聊天界面- 实际的聊天处理可能是通过WebSocket\n\n所以我不应该把chat/send请求转发到Gateway（因为它没有chat/send API）。\n\n正确的方案：\n1. Router 的 chat/send 只处理 intent + score + classify\n2. 返回结果给用户\n3. 用户根据结果决定是否进行下一步（比如调用 LLM）或者，我们可以让 chat/send 返回一个\"就绪\"状态，告诉用户可以进行下一步操作。让我修改代码，只返回 meta 信息，不转发到 Gateway。\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 问题确认\n\n**Gateway (3108) 不是 API 服务**，而是一个 Web UI。它没有 `/chat/send` 端点。\n\n---\n\n### 新方案\n\nRouter 的 `/api/chat/send` 仅返回 **intent + score + classify** 结果，不转发到 Gateway：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d70ff617f1aa73b2b600eaee8f81a","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"newText":"  // 3. 记录元判断日志\n  logMeta({\n    userMessage: userMessage.slice(0, 200),\n    intent: { isTask, confidence },\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: sceneResult\n  });\n  \n  // 返回结果（不转发到 Gateway，因为 Gateway 是 Web UI，不是 API）\n  res.json({\n    success: true,\n    userMessage: userMessage,\n    intent: { isTask, confidence },\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: sceneResult,\n    _message: isTask \n      ? `检测到任务：评分 ${scoreResult?.totalScore || 'N/A'}，场景 ${sceneResult?.label || 'N/A'}`\n      : '已识别为非任务消息'\n  });\n});","oldText":"  // 3. 记录元判断日志\n  logMeta({\n    userMessage: userMessage.slice(0, 200),\n    intent: { isTask, confidence },\n    score: scoreResult,\n    scene: sceneResult\n  });\n  \n  // 转发到 Gateway（不走代理，直接发请求）\n  const gatewayUrl = 'http://127.0.0.1:3108' + req.originalUrl;\n  try {\n    const gatewayResponse = await axios.post(gatewayUrl, req.body, {\n      headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n      timeout: 30000\n    });\n    // 合并结果\n    res.json({\n      ...gatewayResponse.data,\n      _meta: {\n        intent: { isTask, confidence },\n        score: scoreResult,\n        scene: sceneResult\n      }\n    });\n  } catch (err) {\n    console.error(`[Router] Gateway转发失败: ${err.message}`);\n    res.status(502).json({ error: 'Gateway unavailable', details: err.message });\n  }\n});"}],"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":57215,"output":694,"cacheRead":512,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":58421,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775717259017,"responseId":"019d70ff0a21dc38166825cd070d659f"}}
