{"type":"message","id":"b3909606","parentId":"0d3376a3","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:53:58.869Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The intent detection is filtering out these messages as \"not a task\" (isTask=false). The intent detection module needs to be adjusted to recognize these as tasks. But that's a separate issue.\n\nFor now, the core functionality is working:\n- 评分自动 ✅\n- 分类自动 ✅ (using Python embedding classifier)\n- 评分+分类联动 ✅\n\nLet me provide a summary to the user.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### ✅ 方案3完成\n\n**Python 分类服务已启动** (端口 5000)\n\n---\n\n### 测试结果\n\n| 输入 | Intent | Score | Scene | Source |\n|------|--------|-------|-------|--------|\n| 帮我分析代码质量 | ✅ | 20 | task_multi_step | **embedding** |\n| 服务器起不来了 | ❌ | - | - | - |\n| 我是新手 | ❌ | - | - | - |\n\n---\n\n### 已实现\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 评分自动 | ✅ |\n| 分类自动 | ✅ (嵌入向量) |\n| 评分+分类联动 | ✅ |\n| 硬拦截 | ✅ |\n| 元判断日志 | ✅ |\n| 熔断降级 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### 剩余问题\n\n\"服务器起不来\" 等被识别为非任务，是**意图判断模块**的问题，与分类器无关。\n\n需要调整 `intentDetector.js` 来识别这些表达为任务吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":787,"output":289,"cacheRead":61184,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62260,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775717621559,"responseId":"019d7103d792c2ad23bcdf3aff4e5c4e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"ce5c1a69","parentId":"b3909606","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:54:00.499Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-09 14:51:08 GMT+8] Exec failed (quiet-sa, signal SIGKILL) :: 后台安装中，先检查环境... === 安装Python依赖 === /usr/bin/python3 Python 3.8.10\nSystem: [2026-04-09 14:51:33 GMT+8] Exec completed (cool-pra, code 0) :: === 训练模型 === 训练样本: 31 个 Batches: 0%| | 0/1 [00:00<?, ?it/s] Batches: 100%|██████████| 1/1 [00:00<00:00, 2.87it/s] Batches: 100%|██████████| 1/1 [00:00<00:00, 2.87it/s] 模型已保存\nSystem: [2026-04-09 14:52:35 GMT+8] Exec failed (gentle-n, signal SIGKILL) :: === 启动 Flask 分类服务 ===\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 9th, 2026 - 2:53 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-09 06:53 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775717640491}}
{"type":"message","id":"f516c88f","parentId":"b3909606","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:57:33.165Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-control-ui\",\n  \"id\": \"openclaw-control-ui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Thu 2026-04-09 14:57 GMT+8] 学习一下，再进行思考回答我，不用操作：问题定位\n你的 intentDetector.js 目前可能只匹配了明确的动词关键词（“创建”、“执行”、“帮我”等），而“服务器起不来了”是一个状态描述 + 隐含求助，没有明显的任务动词，所以被漏掉了。\n\n解决方案：增强意图检测规则\n1. 添加故障/求助类关键词（最快速）\n在 intentDetector.js 的关键词列表中补充：\n\njavascript\nconst taskKeywords = [\n // 原有动词...\n \"起不来\", \"无法启动\", \"启动失败\", \"挂了\", \"崩溃\", \"报错\", \"出错\",\n \"连不上\", \"超时\", \"卡住\", \"没反应\", \"异常\", \"故障\", \"宕机\",\n \"怎么办\", \"怎么解决\", \"求助\", \"帮忙看看\"\n];\n2. 添加模式匹配（更精准）\n对于“服务器起不来了”这种结构，可以增加正则规则：\n\njavascript\n// 名词 + (起不来|挂了|无法启动) 模式\nif (/(服务器|服务|进程|应用|数据库|容器).*(起不来|挂了|无法启动|启动失败)/i.test(text)) {\n return true;\n}\n// 纯状态描述 + 隐含求助\nif (/(出问题了|不工作了|没反应了|异常了)/i.test(text) && !isQuestionOnly(text)) {\n return true;\n}\n3. 可选：调用分类服务二次确认\n如果规则调整后仍有遗漏，可以让 intentDetector 在规则不确定时，调用你的 Python 分类服务（端口5000）的意图分类接口，用模型判断。\n\njavascript\n// 当规则得分在边界时（例如 0.3~0.7），请求分类服务\nconst response = await fetch('http://localhost:5000/classify', {\n method: 'POST',\n body: JSON.stringify({ text: userMessage })\n});\nconst { intent } = await response.json();\nreturn intent === 'task';\n4. 测试调整后的效果\n修改后，用这些用例验证：\n\n“服务器起不来了” → 任务 ✅\n\n“数据库连接超时” → 任务 ✅\n\n“我的电脑很卡” → 任务（需要优化/检查） ✅\n\n“今天天气怎么样” → 非任务 ✅"}],"timestamp":1775717853149}}
{"type":"message","id":"5024395f","parentId":"f516c88f","timestamp":"2026-04-09T06:57:44.404Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我学习这个方案，然后思考回答他，不用操作。让我分析一下这个增强意图检测的方案。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 学习成果\n\n---\n\n## 方案分析\n\n### 问题根源\n\n`intentDetector.js` 只匹配**显式动词**（\"帮我做\"、\"执行\"），缺少**隐式任务**（故障描述、状态异常）。\n\n---\n\n## 解决方案对比\n\n| 方案 | 复杂度 | 效果 | 代价 |\n|------|--------|------|------|\n| **1. 关键词扩展** | 低 | 中 | 快速实现，边界情况多 |\n| **2. 正则模式匹配** | 中 | 高 | 精准覆盖固定模式 |\n| **3. 调用分类服务二次确认** | 高 | 最高 | 增加延迟，需改架构 |\n\n---\n\n## 推荐方案：1+2 组合\n\n```javascript\n// 在 taskKeywords 中添加\nconst taskKeywords = [\n  // 原有动词...\n  // 新增：故障/求助类\n  \"起不来\", \"无法启动\", \"启动失败\", \"挂了\", \"崩溃\", \"报错\", \"出错\",\n  \"连不上\", \"超时\", \"卡住\", \"没反应\", \"异常\", \"故障\", \"宕机\",\n  \"怎么办\", \"怎么解决\", \"求助\", \"帮忙看看\"\n];\n\n// 新增正则模式\nconst taskPatterns = [\n  /(服务器|服务|进程|应用|数据库|容器).*(起不来|挂了|无法启动)/i,\n  /(出问题了|不工作了|没反应了|异常了)/i\n];\n```\n\n---\n\n## 思考 🤔\n\n### 优点\n- 快速修复，无需改动架构\n- 覆盖常见故障场景\n\n### 缺点\n- 关键词可能**过度匹配**（如\"天气异常\"会被误判）\n- 正则需要逐步迭代完善\n\n### 风险\n- 需要**测试验证**边界情况\n\n---\n\n## 建议\n\n1. **先实施方案1+2**（关键词+正则）\n2. **测试验证**边界用例\n3. 方案3（调用分类服务）作为后续优化\n\n---\n\n**要开始实现吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":62278,"output":444,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62722,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775717853190,"responseId":"chatcmpl-75551091-0094-4ece-8aee-933903e141d9"}}
