{"type":"message","id":"298f11ca","parentId":"f77487d1","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:13:33.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户遇到了一个问题：当他发送包含 HEARTBEAT.md 内容的消息时，似乎导致了卡住。\n\n看消息内容，用户发送的是：\n1. \"为什么这样我就卡住，信息发不出去\"\n2. 系统消息显示 \"Exec failed (tide-she, signal SIGKILL)\"\n3. 然后是 HEARTBEAT.md 的读取结果\n\n这不是我操作导致的卡住，而是用户在发送消息时可能遇到了某种问题。\n\n用户可能是想问：\n1. 为什么系统会显示 Exec failed\n2. 为什么他发不出去消息\n\n从系统消息看，\"Exec failed (tide-she, signal SIGKILL)\" 是在尝试重启 Python 分类服务时发生的，进程被 SIGKILL 终止了。\n\n但这不影响用户发送消息。用户说\"信息发不出去\"可能是指：\n1. UI 问题\n2. 网络问题\n3. 或者之前的 exec 命令虽然失败了但不影响消息发送\n\n让我检查一下当前系统状态，确认消息发送是否正常。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8fda8780796b4278ab4b6bd5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 测试消息发送 ===\" && \\\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d '{\"message\": \"测试消息\"}' | python3 -m json.tool | head -10","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":72034,"output":286,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72320,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775718801635,"responseId":"chatcmpl-6f1a16ea-60fb-4259-ab95-e6b662bd3e27"}}
