{"type":"message","id":"0662d8ff","parentId":"e04312da","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:13:36.128Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"消息发送是正常的。系统返回了正确的结果。\n\n用户看到的 \"Exec failed\" 是之前的 exec 命令被系统终止了，但那是后台执行的命令，不影响消息发送。\n\n让我解释一下发生了什么。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 原因分析\n\n**这不是你卡住了**，而是：\n\n1. **Exec 命令被终止** - `tide-shell` 是我之前执行 `python3 app.py` 的后台进程，它被系统 SIGKILL 终止了（可能因为资源限制或超时）\n\n2. **消息发送正常** - 刚才测试显示消息发送**完全正常**\n\n---\n\n### 当前状态\n\n| 服务 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| Router (3102) | ✅ 正常 |\n| 消息发送 | ✅ 正常 |\n\n---\n\n**你能正常发消息吗？** 如果还是发不出去，可能是 UI 或网络问题。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":72445,"output":173,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775718813711,"responseId":"chatcmpl-47a3e9ce-225a-46a6-9bc0-93c51ff2fa3f"}}
