{"type":"message","id":"8b24b3e7","parentId":"06104ece","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:14:04.660Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说重启网关后才好的。说明之前的某个服务（可能是路由器或网关）出了问题，需要重启才能恢复。这是正常情况，系统已经恢复了。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了 ✅\n\n之前的 Exec 进程被 SIGKILL 终止时，可能影响了路由器的状态，重启 Gateway 后恢复正常。\n\n---\n\n### 总结今天完成的工作\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 方案3混合系统 (Python + Node.js) | ✅ 完成 |\n| 评分自动 | ✅ |\n| 分类自动 | ✅ |\n| 评分+分类联动 | ✅ |\n| 隐式任务识别增强 | ✅ |\n| 硬拦截 | ✅ |\n| 元判断日志 | ✅ |\n| 熔断降级 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n**系统现在正常运行。有其他需要吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":72440,"output":159,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":72599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775718842889,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2d3b9582-3967-463d-b590-466d87aadfb3"}}
