{"type":"message","id":"dc5da2b0","parentId":"60f5e904","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:48:32.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我检查一下架构，看看实际聊天路径是什么。我需要查看 OpenClaw 的配置文件，或者检查一下 WebSocket 处理逻辑。\n\n让我看看 router 里的 WebSocket 升级代码，了解聊天消息是怎么处理的。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"让我检查一下实际的聊天消息入口，特别是 WebSocket 处理。\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2gxs89b4p5jr4butrvf97a4s","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":60,"offset":195,"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775720892746,"responseId":"0217757208925394bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f91ed909"}}
{"type":"message","id":"343ae9aa","parentId":"dc5da2b0","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:48:32.307Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_2gxs89b4p5jr4butrvf97a4s","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    return !req.url.startsWith('/api');\n  },\n  onError: (err, req, res) => {\n    res.status(502).json({ error: 'Gateway unavailable', message: err.message });\n  }\n});\n\napp.use('/', proxy);\n\n// WebSocket Upgrade处理 + 消息拦截\nconst server = require('http').createServer(app);\n\nserver.on('upgrade', (request, socket, head) => {\n  // 保存原始socket，添加监听器\n  const originalSocket = socket;\n  \n  // 包裹socket，捕获所有data事件\n  const originalEmit = socket.emit;\n  socket.emit = function(event, ...args) {\n    if (event === 'data') {\n      const data = args[0];\n      // 调试：打印原始数据前50字节\n      const raw = data.toString();\n      if (raw.length > 0) {\n        console.log(`[Router] WebSocket raw data (${raw.length} bytes): ${raw.slice(0, 50)}${raw.length > 50 ? '...' : ''}`);\n      }\n      try {\n        const msg = JSON.parse(raw);\n        console.log(`[Router] WebSocket parsed: type=${msg.type}, content=${msg.content ? 'yes' : 'no'}`);\n        if (msg.type === 'message' && msg.content) {\n          const userMessage = msg.content;\n          console.log(`[Router] WebSocket message: ${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...`);\n          // 异步检测意图和评分\n          (async () => {\n            const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n            console.log(`[Router] Intent result: isTask=${isTask}, confidence=${confidence}`);\n            if (isTask && confidence >= 0.5) {\n              const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n              const plan = getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1);\n              console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${score.totalScore} → ${plan.mode}`);\n              // 记录指标\n              metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n              metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: plan.mode }).inc();\n              healthChecker.recordTask(plan.mode, score.totalScore);\n            }\n          })();\n        }\n      } catch(e) {\n        console.log(`[Router] WebSocket parse error: ${e.message}`);\n        // 解析失败不影响转发\n      }\n    }\n    return originalEmit.call(this, event, ...args);\n  };\n  \n  proxy.upgrade(request, socket, head);\n});\n\nserver.listen(PORT, () => console.log(`Router on ${PORT} → ${GATEWAY_URL}`));\nconsole.log('[Router] Task Orchestrator v3.0 ready - scoring enabled - intent detection enabled');\n\n[3 more lines in file. Use offset=255 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775720912299}}
{"type":"message","id":"adc83ccf","parentId":"343ae9aa","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:48:57.474Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太棒了！我看到了 WebSocket 的代码！原来：\n\n1. 路由已经有 WebSocket 的监听和消息拦截功能\n2. 在 `server.on('upgrade', ...)` 中有处理 WebSocket 消息的代码\n3. 已经在监听 `msg.type === 'message' && msg.content` 时：\n   - 调用 `detectIntent` 意图判断\n   - 如果是任务且 confidence>=0.5，调用 `computeFineScore` 评分\n   - 但是！没有分类！\n\n所以实际情况是：\n- UI 聊天是通过 WebSocket 的，不是 HTTP /api/chat/send\n- WebSocket 已经有了意图判断和评分，但缺少分类\n- 我需要给 WebSocket 添加分类功能！\n\n让我看看这段代码，然后修改它添加分类功能。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"太好了！我看到了！\n\n---\n\n### 找到聊天入口了！\n\n**实际聊天是通过 WebSocket 传输的**，不是 HTTP /api/chat/send。\n\n---\n\n### 当前状态\n\nWebSocket 代码在 router 中已经有：\n\n| 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 意图判断 | ✅ 已有 |\n| 自动评分 | ✅ 已有 |\n| **自动分类** | ❌ **缺少** |\n\n---\n\n### 需要做的\n\n在 WebSocket 消息处理中添加**分类功能**，就像 HTTP /api/chat/send 那样。\n\n让我修改 WebSocket 代码，添加分类！"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775720912311,"responseId":"0217757209108374bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f9cf74ba"}}
