{"type":"message","id":"231b8d5c","parentId":"ced17f16","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:54:42.951Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到日志里全是 WebSocket 二进制数据的解析错误（这是正常的，因为很多 WebSocket 消息是二进制的），但没有看到 \"Intent result\"、\"检测到任务\"、\"场景识别\" 等日志。\n\n这说明：要么用户还没有在 UI 上发消息，要么我们的修改在重启路由器后没有生效。\n\n让我确认一下：\n1. 我们修改了 WebSocket 代码\n2. 我们重启了路由器\n3. 但是日志中没有看到我们新添加的日志\n\n可能的问题：\n1. 用户还没有在 UI 上发消息\n2. 或者路由器重启后没有正确加载代码\n\n让我直接检查一下，确认我们的修改是正确的，然后给用户一个总结。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"日志里都是 WebSocket 二进制数据解析错误（这是正常的），但没有看到我们新添加的日志（\"Intent result\"、\"检测到任务\"、\"场景识别\"）。\n\n---\n\n### 情况\n\n要么你还没有在 UI 上发消息，要么需要确认代码是否正确。\n\n---\n\n### 我先确认一下代码是否正确\n\n让我检查一下修改：\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_z52vth1dfro0svi5vuzioe85","name":"read","arguments":{"limit":35,"offset":225,"path":"/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775721246970,"responseId":"0217757212456164bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f9f76187"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d8be02ab","parentId":"231b8d5c","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:54:41.923Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_z52vth1dfro0svi5vuzioe85","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"          const userMessage = msg.content;\n          console.log(`[Router] WebSocket message: ${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...`);\n          // 异步检测意图和评分+分类\n          (async () => {\n            const { isTask, confidence } = await detectIntent(userMessage);\n            console.log(`[Router] Intent result: isTask=${isTask}, confidence=${confidence}`);\n            \n            let scoreResult = null;\n            let sceneResult = null;\n            \n            if (isTask && confidence >= 0.5) {\n              const score = await computeFineScore(userMessage);\n              scoreResult = {\n                totalScore: score.totalScore,\n                plan: getExecutionPlan(score.totalScore, score.factors?.scaleIndex || 1)\n              };\n              console.log(`[Router] 检测到任务: \"${userMessage.slice(0,30)}...\" → 评分 ${scoreResult.totalScore} → ${scoreResult.plan.mode}`);\n              metrics.counter('openclaw_tasks_total').inc();\n              metrics.counter('openclaw_task_routes', { mode: scoreResult.plan.mode }).inc();\n              healthChecker.recordTask(scoreResult.plan.mode, scoreResult.totalScore);\n            }\n            \n            // 场景分类（所有消息都分类，用于记录）\n            sceneResult = await sceneClassify(userMessage);\n            console.log(`[Router] 场景识别: ${sceneResult.label} [${sceneResult.meta}]`);\n            \n            // 记录元判断日志\n            logMeta({\n              userMessage: userMessage.slice(0, 200),\n              intent: { isTask, confidence },\n              score: scoreResult,\n              scene: sceneResult\n            });\n          })();\n        }\n\n[16 more lines in file. Use offset=260 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775721281910}}
{"type":"message","id":"d683b1f7","parentId":"d8be02ab","timestamp":"2026-04-09T07:55:04.249Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"代码看起来是正确的。让我确认一下是否有真正的消息进来，或者我们需要换一个方式来测试。\n\n实际上，我刚才看到的日志里只有二进制数据的解析错误，没有正常的 JSON 消息解析成功的日志。这可能是因为：\n\n1. 用户还没有在 UI 上发消息\n2. 或者 WebSocket 消息的结构和我们预期的不一样\n\n让我给用户一个总结，并且建议如何验证。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"代码是正确的！看起来你还没有在 UI 上发消息，或者 WebSocket 消息格式和预期不同。\n\n---\n\n### 已完成的功能\n\n| 入口 | 功能 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **HTTP /api/chat/send** | 意图判断+评分+分类 | ✅ |\n| **WebSocket (UI 聊天)** | 意图判断+评分+分类 | ✅ 代码已写好 |\n| **元判断日志** | 记录所有消息 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n### 验证方式\n\n**方式1**：你现在通过 UI 发一条消息，然后我检查日志\n\n**方式2**：用 HTTP API 手动测试，确认功能正常：\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"帮我分析代码\"}'\n```\n\n---\n\n**你选择哪种方式？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"doubao-seed-2.0-code","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775721281928,"responseId":"0217757212819544bb2d320cfcd0d3dcaa0804120ace3f97f18bc"}}
