{"type":"message","id":"6d9b0f1a","parentId":"aed5c002","timestamp":"2026-04-09T08:10:51.779Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The file doesn't exist, so I need to create it. But the prompt says \"If memory/2026-04-09.md already exists, APPEND new content only\" - since it doesn't exist, I'll create it with the key learnings from today.\n\nLet me summarize the key learnings from today's session:\n\n1. Implemented score-classify联动 (score-classification chain)\n2. Created scene classifier system with 9 scenes\n3. Added critical-interceptor with 6 CRITICAL patterns\n4. Enhanced intent detection to recognize implicit tasks (故障/卡顿)\n5. Added health check and auto-reconnect for classifier service\n6. WebSocket message handling now includes classification\n\nI'll write these to the new file.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1261d6c25e5b47d0a12f3629","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-09.md","content":"# 2026-04-09 工作日志\n\n## 完成任务\n\n### 1. 评分+分类联动系统\n- 实现了评分自动触发 (isTask=true, confidence>=0.5)\n- 实现了分类自动触发 (使用 Python 嵌入分类器)\n- 实现了评分+分类联动 (并行调用)\n\n### 2. 场景分类器 (方案3混合)\n- Python Flask 分类服务 (端口 5000)\n- Node.js 规则分类器作为降级方案\n- 超时保护 (300ms) + 熔断机制 (连续3次失败)\n- 元判断日志 (confidence_threshold=0.5, ambiguity_gap=0.1)\n\n### 3. 意图检测增强\n- 添加隐式任务关键词：起不来/挂了/崩溃/报错/超时/卡住/故障等\n- 添加正则模式匹配：服务器/数据库 + 故障词\n- 添加问题描述类：很卡/很慢/出问题了\n\n### 4. 稳定性优化\n- classifierClient.js 添加健康检查 (30秒间隔)\n- 添加自动重连逻辑 (最多3次)\n- 改进熔断状态管理\n\n### 5. WebSocket 集成\n- 在 WebSocket 消息处理中添加了分类功能\n- UI 聊天消息现在也会自动触发评分+分类\n\n## 关键文件\n\n- Router: /home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js\n- 分类器: /home/ai/openclaw-classifier/\n- 意图检测: /home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js\n- 分类服务: 端口 5000 (Python Flask)\n\n## 待验证\n\n- WebSocket 分类功能需要用户在 UI 上发消息验证\n\n---\n\n*最后更新: 2026-04-09 16:07*"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":