{"type":"message","id":"e9626fa5","parentId":"468a3301","timestamp":"2026-04-09T08:20:07.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是：现在我发信息给他，是否会触发评分和分类？\n\n让我来解释一下现在的状态：\n\n1. HTTP API - /api/chat/send - 会触发评分和分类 ✅\n2. WebSocket - UI聊天 - 代码已经添加了评分和分类，但还没完全验证\n\n用户通过UI发消息是走WebSocket，不是HTTP API。WebSocket的代码我们修改了，但还没有完全验证是否工作。\n\n我应该诚实地告诉用户：\n- 通过HTTP API会触发\n- 通过UI发消息（WebSocket）理论上会触发，但我们还没完全验证\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 现在的状态\n\n| 入口 | 评分 | 分类 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **HTTP /api/chat/send** | ✅ 触发 | ✅ 触发 |\n| **UI 聊天 (WebSocket)** | ⚠️ 代码已加 | ⚠️ 代码已加 |\n\n---\n\n### 实际情况\n\n理论上你应该也可以，但还没完全验证。\n\n**你可以试试**：现在给我发一条消息，我检查日志看看是否触发了评分和分类。\n\n**或者手动测试**：\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:3102/api/chat/send \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"message\": \"帮我重构代码\"}'\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":923,"output":269,"cacheRead":97664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98856,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775722792389,"responseId":"019d71537db902d85e0bd27181155fd2"}}
