{"type":"message","id":"ea208572","parentId":"97153b99","timestamp":"2026-04-09T08:30:45.691Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The result shows:\n- Intent: isTask=False, confidence=-0.5 (because the question has question words like \"吗\")\n- The scene is null because it's not a task\n\nThis confirms that:\n1. The HTTP API works - I can test with it\n2. The message is recognized as NOT a task (because it's a question)\n3. For messages sent directly to me through WebSocket, the logs show they ARE being recorded (for some messages), but maybe not all\n\nThe user is asking: can messages they send to me trigger scoring/classification?\n\nThe answer is: \n- Through HTTP /api/chat/send: YES\n- Through WebSocket (direct chat): Code is added but not fully verified\n\nLet me give a clear answer.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 刚才的消息结果\n\n```\nIntent: isTask=False, confidence=-0.5\n(因为是疑问句，有\"吗\"字)\nScene: null\n```\n\n---\n\n### 回答你的问题\n\n| 方式 | 评分 | 分类 |\n|------|------|------|\n| HTTP `/api/chat/send` | ✅ 可以 | ✅ 可以 |\n| 直接给你发消息 (WebSocket) | ⚠️ 代码有，不确定是否完全生效 |\n\n---\n\n### 验证\n\n刚才你发的 \"我现在给你发信息进行评分和分类吗\"：\n- Intent 检测到了（isTask=False，因为是疑问句）\n- 但没有评分（因为不是任务）\n\n**如果你用 HTTP API 方式发，100% 能触发。**\n\n你现在再试一次？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":110087,"output":317,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":110404,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775723441383,"responseId":"chatcmpl-4dcba0da-f3b1-4b09-9bb4-af6763c17b75"}}
