{"type":"message","id":"1f519382","parentId":"1e940b59","timestamp":"2026-04-09T08:39:21.112Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户让我检查一下今天完成的工作。我应该查看 memory/2026-04-09.md 文件，那里记录了今天的工作内容。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d7164baa271d66c9b15a883d215c2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-04-09.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":3129,"output":69,"cacheRead":111616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114814,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775723951964,"responseId":"019d7164a4ad5f7f3b5d70b019511501"}}
{"type":"message","id":"96c9f313","parentId":"1f519382","timestamp":"2026-04-09T08:39:21.171Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d7164baa271d66c9b15a883d215c2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-04-09 工作日志\n\n## 完成任务\n\n### 1. 评分+分类联动系统\n- 实现了评分自动触发 (isTask=true, confidence>=0.5)\n- 实现了分类自动触发 (使用 Python 嵌入分类器)\n- 实现了评分+分类联动 (并行调用)\n\n### 2. 场景分类器 (方案3混合)\n- Python Flask 分类服务 (端口 5000)\n- Node.js 规则分类器作为降级方案\n- 超时保护 (300ms) + 熔断机制 (连续3次失败)\n- 元判断日志 (confidence_threshold=0.5, ambiguity_gap=0.1)\n\n### 3. 意图检测增强\n- 添加隐式任务关键词：起不来/挂了/崩溃/报错/超时/卡住/故障等\n- 添加正则模式匹配：服务器/数据库 + 故障词\n- 添加问题描述类：很卡/很慢/出问题了\n\n### 4. 稳定性优化\n- classifierClient.js 添加健康检查 (30秒间隔)\n- 添加自动重连逻辑 (最多3次)\n- 改进熔断状态管理\n\n### 5. WebSocket 集成\n- 在 WebSocket 消息处理中添加了分类功能\n- UI 聊天消息现在也会自动触发评分+分类\n\n## 关键文件\n\n- Router: /home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js\n- 分类器: /home/ai/openclaw-classifier/\n- 意图检测: /home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js\n- 分类服务: 端口 5000 (Python Flask)\n\n## 待验证\n\n- WebSocket 分类功能需要用户在 UI 上发消息验证\n\n---\n\n*最后更新: 2026-04-09 16:07*"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775723961163}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc23a4f6","parentId":"96c9f313","timestamp":"2026-04-09T08:39:31.457Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要给用户展示今天完成的工作总结。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 今日完成总结\n\n| # | 任务 | 状态 |\n|---|------|------|\n| 1 | **评分+分类联动系统** | ✅ 完成 |\n| 2 | **场景分类器** (方案3混合) | ✅ 完成 |\n| 3 | **意图检测增强** | ✅ 完成 |\n| 4 | **稳定性优化** | ✅ 完成 |\n| 5 | **WebSocket集成** | ✅ 代码完成 |\n\n---\n\n### 详细\n\n| 功能 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 自动评分 | isTask=true, confidence>=0.5 触发 |\n| 自动分类 | 9种场景，Python嵌入分类器 |\n| 评分+分类联动 | 并行调用 |\n| 隐式任务识别 | 故障/卡顿/问题描述 |\n| 健康检查 | 30秒间隔 |\n| 熔断保护 | 连续3次失败降级 |\n\n---\n\n### 文件位置\n\n| 组件 | 路径 |\n|------|------|\n| Router | `/home/ai/openclaw-router/openclaw-router.js` |\n| 意图检测 | `/home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js` |\n| 分类器 | `/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/` |\n| 日志 | `/home/ai/openclaw-classifier/logs/meta_events.jsonl` |\n\n---\n\n### 待验证\n\n- WebSocket 分类功能（代码已加，未完全验证）"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":115251,"output":307,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115558,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775723961176,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2dc6eb04-49f1-48e4-9cb3-917c04031557"}}
