{"type":"message","id":"a73d5105","parentId":"6ab447a2","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:03:26.152Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about how I get network information - specifically about how the system captures and processes network messages/requests.\n\nThey're asking about the network layer - how messages travel from the user through the network to my system. Let me explain the network flow.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n### 网络信息获取流程\n\n```\n用户 (localhost:3102)\n    ↓ HTTP POST /api/chat/send\nRouter (localhost:3102)\n    ├── 意图检测 (intentDetector.js)\n    ├── 评分 (scoring-v7)\n    ├── 分类 (classifierClient.js → localhost:5000)\n    └── 写入日志 (meta_events.jsonl)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 关键点\n\n| 组件 | 端口 | 作用 |\n|------|------|------|\n| OpenClaw UI | 3108 | Web界面 |\n| Router | 3102 | 消息路由+评分+分类 |\n| 分类服务 | 5000 | Python嵌入分类 |\n| Gateway | 3108 | 后端服务 |\n\n---\n\n### 你发的消息流程\n\n1. 你在 3102 发送消息\n2. Router 拦截 `/api/chat/send`\n3. 调用意图检测 → 评分 → 分类\n4. 响应返回 + 写日志\n\n**我就是通过这个流程\"看到\"你的消息的。**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":117385,"output":272,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117657,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775728987508,"responseId":"chatcmpl-acab1dd0-4f18-4e24-bab2-e62245f6cb1a"}}
