{"type":"message","id":"a0e23aaa","parentId":"a4f279cc","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:03:48.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是如何获取互联网/网络上的信息，比如搜索网页、获取URL内容等。\n\n根据我可用的工具：\n1. web_search - 搜索网页（使用 DuckDuckGo）\n2. web_fetch - 获取URL内容\n\n让我告诉用户我获取互联网信息的方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 互联网信息获取\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **web_search** | 搜索网页（DuckDuckGo） |\n| **web_fetch** | 获取URL内容（HTML→文本） |\n\n---\n\n### 使用方式\n\n```bash\n# 搜索\nweb_search(query=\"最新新闻\")\n\n# 获取网页内容\nweb_fetch(url=\"https://example.com\")\n```\n\n---\n\n### 限制\n\n- 需要用户提供URL或搜索关键词\n- 我不能主动上网搜索（除非你让我搜）\n- 只能获取公开信息\n\n---\n\n**你需要我帮你查什么吗？**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":117669,"output":184,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":117853,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775729026550,"responseId":"chatcmpl-28a121e0-9b9b-4fb6-af56-50317bb2ea7a"}}
