{"type":"message","id":"ac0bb65e","parentId":"276bc7a5","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:04:17.117Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me give the user a summary of useful skills.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 推荐技能\n\n| 类别 | 技能 | 用途 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **效率** | productivity-automation-kit | 工作流模板、日程管理 |\n| **记忆** | ontology | 知识图谱、任务管理 |\n| **长期记忆** | elite-longterm-memory | 持久化记忆 |\n| **编程** | coding-agent | 委托编码任务 |\n| **GitHub** | github-manager | GitHub issues管理 |\n| **自动化** | automation-workflows | 识别自动化机会 |\n| **飞书** | feishu-doc/wiki/drive/perm | 文档、云空间、权限 |\n| **网页** | scrapling | 网页内容提取 |\n| **安全** | critical-interceptor | 危险命令拦截 |\n\n---\n\n### 常用工具\n\n| 工具 | 用途 |\n|------|------|\n| **web_search** | DuckDuckGo搜索 |\n| **web_fetch** | 获取网页内容 |\n| **image** | 图片分析 |\n| **video_generate** | 视频生成 |\n| **summarize** | 摘要/转录 |\n\n---\n\n### 需要我详细介绍哪个？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":118836,"output":249,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119085,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775729052195,"responseId":"chatcmpl-2c6d0ee7-8af5-480e-8541-6bd4ceee9737"}}
