{"type":"message","id":"de065380","parentId":"d08e7bbd","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:05:14.207Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ad4bc791771a462fbf370cbc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Scrapling Skill\n\n> 自适应 Web 爬取框架，用于绕过反爬虫保护\n\n## 安装\n\n```bash\npip install scrapling\n```\n\n## 使用\n\n```python\nfrom scrapling import Fetcher, Parser\n\n# 获取页面\nfetcher = Fetcher()\nresponse = fetcher.get(\"https://example.com\")\n\n# 解析内容\nparser = Parser(response.text)\ntitles = parser.get_text(\"h1\")\n```\n\n## MCP 服务器（可选）\n\n如需 MCP 接口：\n```bash\npip install scrapling-fetch-mcp\nscrapling-fetch-mcp\n```\n\n## 配置\n\n无默认配置，按需调整 fetcher 和 parser 参数。\n\n---\nversion: 1.0"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775729114200}}
