{"type":"message","id":"2ee1503e","parentId":"9b899c34","timestamp":"2026-04-09T10:59:01.406Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"web_fetch 遇到了安全验证页面，无法获取内容。让我尝试其他搜索方式或者直接总结情况。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 结果\n\nPyPI 可能需要人机验证，无法直接获取。\n\n---\n\n### 结论\n\n| 方式 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| pip install scrapling-fetch-mcp | ❌ 找不到包 |\n| PyPI 搜索 | ❌ 页面有验证 |\n\n---\n\n### 建议\n\n| 方案 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 1. 手动安装 | 自己去 pypi.org 搜索下载 |\n| 2. 使用现有工具 | `web_fetch` 已经能用 |\n| 3. 其他爬虫 | beautifulsoup4、requests |\n\n---\n\n你需要我帮你做什么？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":120205,"output":151,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":121508,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775732319484,"responseId":"019d71e4de4f0c5fa6d7ee9ddcfd488a"}}
