{"type":"message","id":"ac1b5e02","parentId":"a91d82d4","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:06:06.158Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"019d71eac6ef2ba8cd2b376977da819b","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"taskSpec\":\"创建两个OpenClaw技能：1) intent-enhancer隐式任务识别技能(包含faultKeywords故障关键词+faultPatterns正则模式) 2) classifier-health技能(包含健康检查+自动重连+熔断机制)，需要编写SKILL.md定义文件并放到~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/目录\",\"score\":20,\"routing\":{\"mode\":\"DIRECT\",\"timeoutSec\":30,\"memLimitMB\":null},\"factors\":{\"instructionCount\":1,\"codeLines\":1,\"dependencyComplexity\":1,\"cpuIntensity\":1,\"ioIntensity\":1,\"networkIntensity\":1,\"estimatedDuration\":1,\"scaleIndex\":1},\"message\":\"Task scored, ready to execute\"}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":40,"aggregated":"{\"taskSpec\":\"创建两个OpenClaw技能：1) intent-enhancer隐式任务识别技能(包含faultKeywords故障关键词+faultPatterns正则模式) 2) classifier-health技能(包含健康检查+自动重连+熔断机制)，需要编写SKILL.md定义文件并放到~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/目录\",\"score\":20,\"routing\":{\"mode\":\"DIRECT\",\"timeoutSec\":30,\"memLimitMB\":null},\"factors\":{\"instructionCount\":1,\"codeLines\":1,\"dependencyComplexity\":1,\"cpuIntensity\":1,\"ioIntensity\":1,\"networkIntensity\":1,\"estimatedDuration\":1,\"scaleIndex\":1},\"message\":\"Task scored, ready to execute\"}","cwd":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775732766148}}
{"type":"message","id":"24ff2f7d","parentId":"ac1b5e02","timestamp":"2026-04-09T11:07:03.527Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Score: 20, mode: DIRECT。让我告诉用户分数，然后开始实现。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n\n### 评分结果\n\n| 项目 | 值 |\n|------|-----|\n| **总分** | **20** |\n| **模式** | **DIRECT** |\n\n，开始创建技能。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"019d71ec2d98d7f6f645c2180b1616e3","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"---\nname: intent-enhancer\ndescription: 增强意图检测识别隐式任务，包括故障类、问题描述类关键词和正则模式匹配。触发词：故障/卡顿/异常等问题识别。\n---\n\n# Intent Enhancer - 隐式任务识别\n\n## 功能\n\n增强 intentDetector.js 的意图检测，识别隐式任务：\n- 故障类关键词（服务器挂了、报错了等）\n- 问题描述类关键词（很卡、很慢、出问题了等）\n- 正则模式匹配\n\n## 触发词\n\n- 故障类：起不来、挂了、崩溃、报错、连不上、超时、卡住、故障、宕机\n- 问题描述：很卡、很慢、反应慢、出问题了、有问题\n- 求助类：怎么办、怎么解决、求助、帮忙看看\n\n## 实现\n\n在 intentDetector.js 中添加：\n\n```javascript\nconst RULE = {\n  faultKeywords: /(起不来|无法启动|启动失败|挂了|崩溃|报错|出错|连不上|超时|卡住|没反应|异常|故障|宕机|怎么办|怎么解决|求助|帮忙看看|很卡|卡|慢|反应慢|响应慢|有问题|出问题了|出故障)/i,\n  faultPatterns: [\n    /(服务器|服务|进程|应用|数据库|容器|网站|系统).*(起不来|挂了|无法启动|启动失败|崩溃|宕机)/i,\n    /(数据库|mysql|redis|mongodb|nginx).*(连不上|连接超时|报错|异常)/i,\n    /(磁盘|硬盘|空间|内存|cpu).*(满了|不足|占用|爆了)/i,\n    /.*(起不来|挂了|不工作|没反应|异常了)$/i,\n    /(怎么办|怎么解决|求助|帮忙看看)/i\n  ]\n};\n\nfunction ruleBasedScore(message) {\n  let score = 0;\n  // ... 原有关键词 ...\n  // 新增：故障关键词\n  if (RULE.faultKeywords.test(message)) score += 2;\n  // 新增：故障模式\n  for (const pattern of RULE.faultPatterns) {\n    if (pattern.test(message)) {\n      score += 2;\n      break;\n    }\n  }\n  return score;\n}\n```\n\n## 测试用例\n\n| 输入 | 预期结果 |\n|------|----------|\n| 服务器起不来了 | isTask=true |\n| 我的电脑很卡 | isTask=true |\n| 系统出问题了 | isTask=true |\n| 今天天气怎么样 | isTask=false |\n| 帮我分析代码 | isTask=true |\n\n## 文件位置\n\n- 修改: `/home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js`\n- 备份: `/home/ai/openclaw-router/intentDetector.js.bak`","path":"/home/ai/.openclaw/workspace/skills/intent-enhancer/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"codingplan","model":"minimax-m2.5","usage":{"input":123263,"output":686,"cacheRead":1152,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":125101,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1775732766164,"responseId":"019d71ebadc6a4075077ee70a23b0287"}}
